cumstances-ahead-of-2024-lok-sabha-elections-5255406%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanother-blow-to-kcr-chevella-mp-ranjith-reddy-quits-brs-over-current-political-circumstances-ahead-of-2024-lok-sabha-elections-5255406%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanother-blow-to-kcr-chevella-mp-ranjith-reddy-quits-brs-over-current-political-circumstances-ahead-of-2024-lok-sabha-elections-5255406%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20US's%20Remarks%20On%20CAA%2C%20S%20Jaishankar%20Cites%20%26quot%3BNumber%20Of%20Examples%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20criticism%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%20(CAA)%20from%20the%20US%20and%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20globe%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20has%20said%20it%20is%20important%20to%20put%20it%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20Partition%2C%20and%20underlined%20that%20there%20are%20a%20%26quot%3Bnumber%20of%20examples%26quot%3B%20in%20which%20many%20countries%20have%20fast-tracked%20citizenship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20an%20interaction%20at%20the%20India%20Today%20Conclave%202024%20on%20Saturday%2C%20he%20also%20responded%20to%20questions%20on%20an%20Indian%20national%2C%20facing%20charges%20in%20a%20murder-for-hire%20plot%20to%20kill%20a%20Khalistani%20separatist%20on%20American%20soil%20and%20US%20Ambassador%20Eric%20Garcetti's%20remarks%20a%20day%20earlier%20on%20its%20impact%20on%20US-India%20ties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20keep%20using%20India%20and%20Canada%20seamlessly%2C%20I%20would%20draw%20a%20line%20there%2C%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20reasons.%20Most%20notably%20that%20all%20said%20and%20done%2C%20American%20politics%20has%20not%20given%20that%20kind%20of%20space%20to%20violent%20extremist%20views%20and%20activities%20which%20Canada%20has%20done.%20So%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20it's%20fair%20to%20the%20US%2C%20to%20lump%20them%20together.%20I%20would%20distinguish%20between%20the%20two%2C%26quot%3B%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20relations%20between%20India%20and%20Canada%20saw%20bitterness%20last%20year%20over%20allegations%20linked%20with%20the%20killing%20of%20Khalistani%20separatist%20and%20designated%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20in%20June%20in%20the%20Canadian%20city%20of%20Surrey.%20India%20denied%20the%20allegation%20as%20%26quot%3Babsurd%20and%20motivated%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaishankar%20also%20responded%20to%20criticisms%20surrounding%20the%20CAA%20from%20Washington%20and%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20on%20Thursday%20said%20it%20is%20concerned%20about%20the%20notification%20of%20CAA%20in%20India%20and%20is%20closely%20monitoring%20its%20implementation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%2C%20I%20am%20not%20questioning%20the%20imperfections%20or%20otherwise%20of%20their%20democracy%20or%20their%20principles%20or%20lack%20of%20it.%20I%20am%20questioning%20their%20understanding%20of%20our%20history.%20If%20you%20hear%20comments%20from%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20world%2C%20it%20is%20as%20if%20the%20Partition%20of%20India%20never%20happened%2C%20there%20were%20no%20consequential%20problems%20which%20the%20CAA%20is%20supposed%20to%20address%2C%26quot%3B%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20if%20you%20take%20a%20problem%20and%20%26quot%3Bremove%20all%20the%20historical%20context%20from%20it%2C%20sanitise%20it%20and%20make%20it%20into%20a%20political%20correctness%26quot%3B%20argument%2C%20and%20say%2C%20'I%20have%20principles%20and%20don't%20you%20have%20principles'%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20principles%20too%2C%20and%20one%20of%20them%20is%20obligation%20to%20people%20who%20were%20let%20down%20at%20the%20time%20of%20Partition.%20And%2C%20I%20think%2C%20the%20Home%20Minister%20spoke%20very%20eloquently%20on%20it%20yesterday%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGarcetti%20in%20response%20to%20a%20question%20on%20CAA%20during%20a%20panel%20discussion%20at%20the%20conclave%20on%20Friday%2C%20had%20said%20the%20principles%20of%20religious%20freedom%20and%20of%20equality%20under%20the%20law%20is%20a%20cornerstone%20of%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%2C%20that%20is%20why%20we%20look%20at%20these%20things%2C%20it%20will%20be%20easier%20not%20to%20look%20at%20our%20friends.%20We%20invite%20you%20to%20do%20the%20same%20with%20our%20imperfect%20democracy%2C%20it%20is%20not%20a%20one-way%20street.%20But%2C%20you%20cannot%20give%20up%20on%20principles%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20close%20you%20are%20with%20friends...%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaishankar%20while%20responding%20to%20the%20criticism%20on%20CAA%2C%20also%20cited%20a%20%26quot%3Bnumber%20of%20examples%26quot%3B%20to%20make%20his%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20has%20a%20problem%20when%20people%20don't%20hold%20up%20a%20mirror%20to%20their%20own%20policies%2C%20as%20he%20cited%20Jackson-Vanik%20amendment%2C%20which%20was%20about%20Jews%20from%20Soviet%20Union%2C%20the%20Lautenberg%20Amendment%2C%20Specter%20Amendment%20and%20%26quot%3Bfast-tracking%20of%20Hungarians%20after%20the%20Hungarian%20revolution%2C%20fast-tracking%20of%20Cubans%20in%201960s%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20if%20you%20were%20to%20ask%20me%2C%20have%20other%20countries%2C%20other%20democracies%2C%20fast-tracked%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20ethnicity%2C%20faith%2C%20social%20attributes%2C%20I%20can%20give%20you%20any%20number%20of%20examples%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20sought%20to%20put%20the%20context%20of%20the%201947%20Partition%20which%20cleaved%20the%20Indian%20subcontinent%20into%20two%20independent%20nations%20India%20and%20Pakistan%2C%20and%20led%20to%20a%20massive%20bloodshed%20resulting%20in%20large-scale%20migrations%20across%20the%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20if%20I%20were%20to%20also%20say%2C%20after%20all%20why%20is%20the%20situation%20important%2C%20because%20very%20often%20when%20you%20have%20something%20very%20cataclysmic%2C%20something%20really%20very%20major%2C%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20to%20deal%20with%20all%20the%20consequences%20right%20then%20and%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20leadership%20of%20this%20country%20had%20promised%20to%20these%20minorties%2C%20that%20if%20you%20have%20a%20problem%2C%20you%20are%20welcome%20to%20come%20to%20India.%20The%20leadership%20thereafter%20didn't%20deliver%20on%20the%20promise%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaishankar%20said%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20just%20our%20predicament.%20If%20you%20look%20at%20Europe%2C%20many%20European%20countries%20fast-tracked%20citizenship%20of%20people%20who%20were%20left%20behind%20on%20the%20World%20War%20or%20in%20some%20cases%20much%20before%20the%20World%20War%20Some%20historical%20issues%20which%20were%20not%20addressed...I%20have%20a%20moral%20obligation%20to%20that%20community%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20the%20world%20is%20full%20of%20examples%2C%20and%20to%20me%20the%20context%20therefore%20is%20very%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20upcoming%20US%20elections%2C%20the%20Union%20minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20are%20prepared%20for%20whatever%20happens%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20actually%20built%20a%20very%20extensive%20culture%20of%20engaging%20and%20sort%20of%20maintaining%20relationships...Well%20before%20the%202016%20November%20results%2C%20we%20had%20already%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20Trump%20campaign%20at%20a%20high%20level.%20Because%2C%20that%20is%20the%20way%20it%20would%20be.%20It%20wouldn't%20be%20hypothetically%20tomorrow%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBecause%20the%20US-India%20relationship%20is%20%26quot%3Bvery%20important%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20is%20the%20only%20way%20one%20can%20get%20a%20grip%20on%20that%20relationship%2C%20the%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20Indian%20national%2C%20facing%20charge%20for%20a%20murder-for-hire%20plot%20to%20kill%20a%20Khalistani%20separatist%20on%20American%20soil%2C%20he%20also%20shared%20how%20India%20is%20dealing%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20the%20US%20has%20shared%20with%20us%20some%20information%2C%20some%20of%20this%20in%20the%20public%20domain%2C%20some%20of%20it%20is%20not.%20And%2C%20our%20interest%20is%20to%20also%20look%20into%20it%2C%20because%2C%20to%20us%20there%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20very%20strong%20organised%20crime%20aspect%20to%20it%20which%20also%20impinges%20on%20our%20own%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20when%20we%20were%20apprised%20of%20this%20information%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20set%20up%20a%20very%20high-power%20committee%20of%20competent%20people%20to%20look%20into%20it%20and%20that%20is%20an%20ongoing%20issue%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20came%20up%20with%20some%20light-hearted%20response%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20use%20of%20social%20media%20and%20diplomacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%2C%20I%20am%20paid%20to%20fix%20foreign%20policy%2C%20I%20am%20not%20paid%20to%20fix%20social%20media%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20drawing%20laughter%20from%20the%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20be%20honest%20no%20one%20can%20fix%20social%20media.%20The%20nature%20of%20the%20platform%20is%20such%20that%20every%20thing%20that%20you%20somewhat%20disapprovingly%20state%20is%20actually%20something%20that%20gets%20more%20eyeballs%20on%20social%20media%2C%26quot%3B%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20assumed%20this%20is%20a%20medium%20which%20is%20very%20angular%2C%20but%20one%20can%20counter%20it%20fairly%20rapidly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20(MEA)%20have%20adjusted%20to%20the%20times%20too...Short%2C%20sharp%20impactful%20expressions%20(on%20social%20media)%20are%20re