ella%20Hammad%2C%20Maaza%20Mengiste%2C%20Zaina%20Arafat%20and%20Susan%20Muaddi%20Darraj%20are%20among%20the%20signatories%20of%20the%20letter%20that%20also%20urges%20other%20writers%20to%20reconsider%20their%20decision%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20festival%20is%20touted%20as%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20high%20profile%20literary%20events%20and%20has%20been%20organised%20annually%20since%202005.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20context%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20ongoing%20war%20on%20Gaza%2C%20we%20believe%20that%20PEN%20America%20has%20betrayed%20the%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20professed%20commitment%20to%20peace%20and%20equality%20for%20all%2C%20and%20to%20freedom%20and%20security%20for%20writers%20everywhere%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20letter%20reads.%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20letter%20also%20calls%20out%20PEN%20America%E2%80%99s%20reluctance%20to%20join%20other%20human%20rights%20organisations%20in%20demanding%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20two%20prominent%20novelists%20also%20severed%20ties%20with%20the%20group%20over%20its%20decision%20to%20platform%20Mayim%20Bialik%2C%20a%20vocal%20opponent%20of%20ceasefire%20efforts%2C%20at%20a%20PEN%20Out%20Loud%20event%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%20The%20removal%20of%20Palestinian-American%20writer%20Randa%20Jarrar%20from%20the%20same%20event%20further%20fueled%20criticism%20of%20the%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20Jarrar%E2%80%99s%20removal%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2F600-writers-poets-urge-pen-america-to-do-the-bare-minimum-for-palestinian-authors%5C%22%3Ea%20group%20of%20600%20writers%20and%20poets%20signed%20an%20open%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E%20condemning%20PEN%E2%80%99s%20relative%20silence%20on%20Gaza.%20That%20letter%20has%20now%20been%20signed%20by%20more%20than%201300%20writers%2C%20including%20Roxane%20Gay%2C%20Lauren%20Groff%2C%20Marie-Helene%20Bertino%2C%20Kiese%20Laymon%2C%20Saeed%20Jones%2C%20Carmen%20Maria%20Machado%2C%20Solmaz%20Sharif%2C%20Tommy%20Pico%2C%20Laura%20van%20den%20Berg%2C%20and%20Nana%20Kwame%20Adjei-Brenyah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20full%20text%20of%20the%20letter%20is%20produced%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMarch%2013%2C%202024%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20of%20us%20was%20invited%20to%20take%20part%20in%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20PEN%20World%20Voices%20festival%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%20as%20speakers%2C%20moderators%20and%20as%20an%20honorary%20co-chair.%20We%20have%20decided%20not%20to%20participate.%20This%20letter%20explains%20why%20our%20conscience%20leaves%20us%20no%20other%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20would%20have%20welcomed%20the%20prospect%20of%20gathering%20with%20our%20colleagues%20from%20around%20the%20world%20to%20share%20insights%20and%20combine%20our%20strengths%2C%20which%20was%20why%20most%20of%20us%20accepted%20the%20invitation%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20PEN%20World%20Voices%20Festival%20when%20it%20was%20initially%20extended.%20While%20aware%20that%20PEN%20America%20has%20often%20been%20missing-in-action%20when%20Palestinian%20speech%20was%20under%20attack%2C%20we%20held%20out%20hope%20that%20this%20was%20changing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20in%20the%20months%20since%20that%20initial%20invitation%2C%20we%20have%20concluded%20that%20attending%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20festival%20would%20only%20serve%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20illusion%20that%20PEN%20America%20is%20truly%20devoted%20to%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20defence%20of%20free%20speech%20at%20the%20center%20of%20humanity%E2%80%99s%20struggle%20against%20repression%2C%E2%80%9D%20as%20it%20has%20claimed.%20In%20the%20context%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20ongoing%20war%20on%20Gaza%2C%20we%20believe%20that%20PEN%20America%20has%20betrayed%20the%20organization%E2%80%99s%20professed%20commitment%20to%20peace%20and%20equality%20for%20all%2C%20and%20to%20freedom%20and%20security%20for%20writers%20everywhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PEN%20charter%2C%20adopted%20in%201948%2C%20states%20that%20it%20is%20the%20duty%20of%20PEN%20members%20to%20%E2%80%9Cto%20do%20their%20utmost%20to%20dispel%20all%20hatreds%20and%20to%20champion%20the%20ideal%20of%20one%20humanity%20living%20in%20peace%20and%20equality%20in%20one%20world.%E2%80%9D%20Unfortunately%2C%20it%20has%20become%20painfully%20clear%20that%2C%20for%20PEN%20America%2C%20Palestine%20continues%20to%20be%20an%20exception%20to%20this%20ideal.%20Palestine%E2%80%99s%20poets%2C%20scholars%2C%20novelists%20and%20journalists%20and%20essayists%20have%20risked%20everything%2C%20including%20their%20lives%20and%20the%20lives%20of%20their%20families%2C%20to%20share%20their%20words%20with%20the%20world.%20Yet%20PEN%20America%20appears%20unwilling%20to%20stand%20with%20them%20firmly%20against%20the%20powers%20that%20have%20oppressed%20and%20dispossessed%20them%20for%20the%20last%2075%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20you%20know%2C%20an%20unrelenting%20genocidal%20campaign%20is%20currently%20being%20waged%20against%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%2C%20a%20horror%20that%20has%20been%20filmed%20daily%20and%20streamed%20live%20around%20the%20world.%20More%20than%20100%2C000%20people%20have%20been%20injured%2C%20and%20more%20than%2030%2C000%20killed%2C%20including%20over%2012%2C000%20children.%20More%20than%2070%20percent%20of%20the%20homes%20in%20Gaza%20have%20been%20damaged%20or%20destroyed%2C%20leaving%20more%20than%20a%20million%20people%20homeless%20in%20a%20land%20where%20nowhere%20is%20safe%20from%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20drones%2C%20missiles%2C%20bombs%2C%20and%20bullets%2C%20in%20part%20paid%20for%20and%20supplied%20by%20the%20United%20States%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20the%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%20found%20it%20plausible%20that%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20siege%20on%20Gaza%20could%20amount%20to%20genocide%20and%20ordered%20%E2%80%9Cimmediate%20and%20effective%20measures%E2%80%9D%20to%20protect%20Palestinians%20in%20the%20occupied%20territories%20by%20ensuring%20sufficient%20humanitarian%20assistance%20and%20enabling%20basic%20services.%20Thousands%20more%20Palestinian%20adults%20and%20children%20have%20been%20killed%20since%20the%20ICJ%20ruling%3B%20not%20only%20has%20Israel%20refused%20to%20facilitate%20adequate%20aid%2C%20it%20has%20actually%20hindered%20it.%C2%A0%20Hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%20are%20at%20risk%20of%20famine%2C%20and%20a%20growing%20number%20of%20children%20and%20elderly%20people%20are%20dying%20of%20malnutrition%20and%20dehydration%20even%20after%20they%20survive%20the%20bombing%20of%20their%20homes.%20Despite%20all%20this%2C%20PEN%20America%20has%20declined%20to%20join%20other%20leading%20human%20rights%20organizations%20and%20United%20Nations%20officials%20in%20the%20demands%20for%20an%20immediate%20and%20unconditional%20ceasefire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20failure%20is%20particularly%20striking%20in%20light%20of%20the%20extraordinary%20toll%20this%20catastrophe%20has%20taken%20in%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmesana.org%2Fadvocacy%2Fletters-from-the-board%2F2024%2F03%2F11%2Fmesa-board-joint-statement-with-caf-regarding-the-ongoing-genocidal-violence-against-the-palestinian-people-and-their-cultural-heritage-in-gaza%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecultural%20sphere%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Israel%20has%20killed%2C%20and%20at%20times%20deliberately%20targeted%20and%20assassinated%20journalists%2C%20poets%2C%20novelists%2C%20and%20writers%20of%20all%20kinds.%20It%20has%20destroyed%20almost%20all%20forms%20of%20cultural%20infrastructure%20that%20support%20the%20practice%20of%20literature%2C%20art%2C%20intellectual%20exchange%2C%20and%20free%20speech%20through%20the%20bombing%20and%20demolition%20of%20universities%2C%20cultural%20centers%2C%20museums%2C%20libraries%2C%20and%20printing%20presses.%20By%20disrupting%20access%20to%20digital%20communication%2C%20Israel%20has%20also%20been%20blocking%20Palestinians%20from%20sharing%20what%20they%20have%20witnessed%20and%20experienced%20and%20telling%20the%20truth%20of%20what%20is%20happening%20to%20them.%20Everyone%20who%20uses%20the%20power%20of%20the%20pen%20and%20free%20speech%20to%20appeal%20to%20the%20conscience%20of%20the%20world%20is%20at%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20less%20than%20five%20months%2C%20Israel%20has%20killed%20nearly%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcpj.org%2F2024%2F03%2Fjournalist-casualties-in-the-israel-gaza-conflict%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20hundred%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0journalists%20and%20media%20workers%2C%20more%20than%20in%20the%20two-decade%20war%20in%20Afghanistan%2C%20and%20more%20than%20in%20the%20deadliest%20year%20of%20the%20Iraq%20War.%20Israel%20has%20also%20killed%20nearly%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feuromedmonitor.org%2Fen%2Farticle%2F6108%2FIsrael-kills-dozens-of-academics%2C-destroys-every-university-in-the-Gaza-Strip%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20hundred%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0academics%20and%20writers.%20If%20organizations%20like%20PEN%20America%20cling%20to%20the%20illusion%20of%20political%20neutrality%20in%20the%20face%20of%20a%20clear%20effort%20to%20destroy%20Palestinian%20lives%20and%20culture%2C%20one%20can%20only%20wonder%20whether%20there%20will%20be%20any%20writers%20left%20in%20Gaza%20to%20tell%20the%20story%20of%20their%20apocalypse%2C%20or%20to%20trust%20words%20and%20speech%2C%20when%20the%20killing%20finally%20ends.%20Or%20any%20record%20left%20of%20the%20history%20they%20have%20lived.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScholars%20are%20increasingly%20reaching%20for%20novel%20words%20to%20describe%20the%20scope%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20cultural%20genocide.%20Words%20like%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fthe-war-in-gaza-is-wiping-out-palestines-education-and-knowledge-systems-222055%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escholasticide%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20are%20invoked%20to%20describe%20the%20elimination%20of%20systems%20of%20education%20and%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.palestine-studies.org%2Fen%2Fnode%2F1655161%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eepistemicide%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20to%20describe%20the%20erasure%20of%20systems%20of%20knowledge.%20In%20contrast%2C%20PEN%20America%2C%20took%20four%20and%20half%20months%20to%20utter%20the%20word%20%E2%80%9Cceasefire%2C%E2%80%9D%20then%20only%20with%20a%20vague%20%E2%80%9Chope%E2%80%9D%20for%20one%20that%20is%20%E2%80%9Cmutually%20agreed%2C%E2%80%9D%20rather%20than%20a%20clear%20call.%20We%20expect%20more%20from%20an%20organization%20that%20exists%20for%20the%20express%20purpose%20of%20protecting%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20thought%2C%20and%20advancing%20a%20vision%20of%20our%20common%20humanity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEqually%20concerning%20is%20PEN%20America%E2%80%99s%20history%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpen.org%2Fpress-release%2Fpen-america-statement-sally-rooney-turning-down-hebrew-translation-novel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econdemning%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0authors%20who%20choose%20to%20honor%20the%20Palestinian%20call%20for%20a%20cultural%20and%20academic%20boycott%20of%20Israeli%20institutions%20complicit%20in%20their%20oppression%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20impeding%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20free%20flow%20of%20ideas.%E2%80%9D%20It%20seems%20to%20us%20that%20this%20violates%20several%20principles%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20PEN%E2%80%99s%20mission.%20To%20begin%20with%2C%20the%20idea%20that%20BDS%2C%20which%20does%20not%20boycott%20individual%20writers%20or%20scholars%2C%20can%20impede%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfree%20flow%20of%20ideas%E2%80%9D%20in%20Israel-Palestine%20assumes%20that%20such%20a%20thing%20exists%20there.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20is%20a%20cruel%20fantasy%20so%20long%20as%20Palestinians%20live%20under%20a%20rule%20reliant%20on%20racial%20segregation%20and%20the%20implementation%20of%20ethnic%20hierarchies%2C%20siege%20and%20collective%20punishment%2C%20the%20very%20conditions%20BDS%20seeks%20to%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20condemning%20authors%20who%20choose%20to%20support%20BDS%20contradicts%20PEN%E2%80%99s%20own%20mandate%20to%20protect%20freedom%20of%20expression%2C%20as%20it%20contributes%20to%20a%20neo-McCarthyite%20environment%20in%20North%20America%20and%20Europe%2C%20in%20which%20the%20growing%20support%20for%20BDS%20is%20increasingly%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpalestinelegal.org%2Fnews%2F2022%2F11%2F14%2Fnew-resource-on-the-right-to-boycott%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecriminalized%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Third%2C%20opposition%20to%20BDS%20overlooks%20the%20long%20and%20proud%20history%20of%20the%20boycott%20as%20an%20effective%2C%20nonviolent%20tool%20of%20collective%20liberation.%20Just%20as%20boycott%20was%20a%20principal%20tool%20used%20to%20successfully%20end%20political%20apartheid%20in%20South%20Africa%2C%20so%20it%20should%20be%20accepted%20that%20some%20are%20free%20to%20adopt%20it%20as%20a%20vital%20tool%20in%20the%20nonviolent%20resistance%20movement%20against%20Israeli%20impunity%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20aware%20that%20PEN%20America%20has%20posted%20a%20series%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpen.org%2Fregion%2Fisrael-gaza%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatements%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0expressing%20concern%20about%20various%20incidents%20in%20Gaza.%20We%20have%20also%20followed%20the%20organization%E2%80%99s%20attempts%20to%20quell%20a%20wave%20of%20criticism%20from%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flithub.com%2Fover-600-writers-have-signed-this-open-letter-to-pen-america%2F%5C%22%3Ehundreds%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0of%20outraged%20writers%20by%20issuing%20a%20statement%20hoping%20for%20peace.%20While%20we%20object%20to%20the%20ahistoricism%20and%20false%20equivalencies%20in%20PEN%E2%80%99s%20portrayal%20of%20the%20war%20and%20its%20causes%2C%20our%20overarching%20question%20is%20this%3A%20Where%20are%20the%20actions%20that%20flow%20from%20these%20stated%20concerns%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPEN%20America%20has%20not%20launched%20any%20substantial%20coordinated%20support%20or%20issued%20any%20reports%20highlighting%20the%20scale%20and%20scope%20of%20the%20attacks%20on%20writers%20in%20Gaza%2C%20or%20on%20Palestinian%20speech%20and%20culture%20more%20broadly.%20PEN%20America%20has%20done%20very%20little%20to%20mobilize%20or%20inspire%20its%20many%20members%E2%80%94quite%20unlike%20recent%20PEN%20America%20campaigns%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpen.org%2Fregion%2Fukraine%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopposing%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20its%20impact%20on%20culture%2C%20or%20PEN%20International%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9CDay%20of%20the%20Dead%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pen-international.org%2Four-campaigns%2Fday-of-the-dead-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehonouring%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0journalists%20killed%20in%20Latin%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20know%20that%20some%20will%20claim%20that%20by%20choosing%20to%20not%20take%20part%20in%20PEN%20World%20Voices%20Festival%2C%20we%20obstruct%20free%20speech%2C%20or%20that%20we%20think%20that%20PEN%20should%20only%20platform%20writers%20with%20whom%20we%20agree.%20Nothing%20could%20be%20further%20from%20the%20truth.%20We%20ask%20only%20that%20PEN%20America%20abide%20by%20its%20own%20principles%20and%20charter%20with%20consistency%20and%20live%20up%20to%20its%20core%20mandate%20to%20clearly%20and%20courageously%20defend%20the%20writers%20most%20at%20risk%20from%20repression%20and%20threat%20of%20being%20murdered.%20When%20the%20organization%20fails%20to%20do%20so%2C%20other%20writers%20will%20inevitably%20organize%20to%20fill%20its%20silences%E2%80%94including%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flithub.com%2Fpalestinian-american-writer-randa-jarrar-was-dragged-out-of-a-pen-event%2F%5C%22%3Ein%20ways%20that%20disrupt%20PEN%20itself%3C%2Fa%3E.%20When%20those%20moments%20occur%2C%20it%20is%20morally%20vacuous%20to%20wag%20fingers%20at%20those%20who%20are%20speaking%20truth%20to%20power%20in%20a%20disruptive%20fashion.%20We%20are%20dismayed%20that%20there%20has%20been%20no%20apology%20to%20the%20Palestinian%20writer%20Randa%20Jarrar%20for%20the%20shocking%20act%20of%20dragging%20her%20out%20of%20an%20event%20featuring%20an%20anti-Palestinian%20and%20pro-war%20Hollywood%20actor%20as%20Jarrar%20read%20out%20the%20names%20of%20murdered%20Palestinian%20writers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20global%20network%20of%20PEN%20chapters%20and%20PEN%20International%20has%20a%20long%20history%20of%20providing%20a%20safe%20haven%20for%20artists%20under%20siege.%20It%20has%20not%20only%20saved%20individual%20lives%20by%20evacuating%20writers%20from%20danger%20zones%20(including%20from%20Gaza)%20but%20has%20created%20gatherings%20where%20writers%20under%20attack%20can%20experience%20the%20warmth%20of%20genuine%20solidarity%20from%20the%20global%20literary%20community.%20Palestinian%20writers%20deserve%20that%20kind%20of%20respite.%20Instead%2C%20many%20have%20found%20themselves%20in%20the%20insulting%20position%20of%20having%20to%20fight%20PEN%20America%20to%20loudly%20call%20for%20the%20U.S.-funded%20bombs%20to%20stop%20falling.%20They%20have%20been%20forced%20to%20point%20out%2C%20over%20and%20over%20again%2C%20that%20if%20the%20current%20onslaught%20was%20directed%20against%20any%20other%20people%2C%20there%20would%20have%20been%20clear%20condemnations%20of%20the%20crimes%2C%20as%20well%20as%20support%20for%20all%20forms%20of%20nonviolent%20resistance%20against%20oppression%2C%20alongside%20events%20focused%20on%20the%20artists%20who%20are%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20seen%20that%20PEN%20America%20can%20be%20open%20to%20criticism%20and%20has%20responded%20by%20adding%20new%20pages%20to%20its%20website%20and%20issuing%20new%20statements.%20This%20is%20welcome%20but%20still%20not%20enough%2C%20and%20sadly%20too%20late%20for%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20PEN%20World%20Voices%20Festival%20to%20live%20up%20to%20this%20critical%20historical%20moment.%20We%20hope%20that%20our%20decision%20not%20to%20participate%20will%20add%20to%20existing%20efforts%20to%20yield%20concrete%20and%20lasting%20change%20at%20a%20time%20that%20calls%20for%20moral%20courage%20from%20us%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMichelle%20Alexander%2C%20author%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20New%20Jim%20Crow%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3EZaina%20Arafat%2C%20author%C2%A0%3Cem%3EYou%20Exist%20Too%20Much%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3EKristen%20Arnett%2C%20author%C2%A0%3Cem%3EWith%20Teeth%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3ESimone%20Brown%2C%20author%C2%A0%3Cem%3EDark%20Matters%3A%20On%20the%20Surveillance%20of%20Blackness%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3EMichael%20Elias%2C%20author%C2%A0%3Cem%3EYou%20Can%20Go%20Home%20Now%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3EKay%20Gabriel%2C%20editorial%20director%20The%20Poetry%20Project%3Cem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3EIsabella%20Hammad%2C%20author%C2%A0%3Cem%3EEnter%20Ghost%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3EBalsam%20Karam%2C%20author%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Singularity%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3EDima%20Khalidi%2C%20director%20Palestine%20Legal%3Cem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3ENaomi%20Klein%2C%20author%C2%A0%3Cem%3EDoppelganger%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3EHisham%20Matar%2C%20author%C2%A0%3Cem%3EMy%20Friends%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3EMaaza%20Mengiste%2C%20author%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Shadow%20King%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3ELorrie%20Moore%2C%20author%C2%A0%3Cem%3EI%20Am%20Homeless%20if%20This%20Is%20Not%20My%20Home%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3ESusan%20Muaddi%20Darraj%2C%20author%C2%A0%3Cem%3EA%20Curious%20Land%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fe