e%20at%20a%20fashion%20show%20garnered%20attention%2C%20particularly%20her%20humorous%20response%20to%20a%20paparazzo's%20comment%20on%20her%20'wedding%20glow.'%20In%20a%20viral%20video%2C%20she%20amusingly%20questioned%20if%20her%20glow%20was%20absent%20before%20marriage.%20Rakul%20also%20shared%20a%20comical%20incident%20involving%20her%20father's%20meeting%20with%20her%20husband-to-be%2C%20Jackky.%20They%20tied%20the%20knot%20in%20Goa%20after%20dating%20for%20three%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Is%20Delhi%20Jal%20Board%20Case%20In%20Which%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20Got%20Fresh%20Summons%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20legal%20tussle%20between%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20over%20the%20multiple%20summonses%20in%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20case%2C%20the%20central%20agency%20has%20now%20asked%20the%20AAP%20leader%20to%20appear%20for%20questioning%20in%20another%20case.%C2%A0Mr%20Kejriwal%20has%20been%20summoned%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20linked%20to%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20Delhi%20Jal%20Board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20Delhi%20Jal%20Board%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESet%20up%20in%201998%2C%20the%20Delhi%20Jal%20Board%20is%20responsible%20for%20distributing%20drinking%20water%20across%20the%20national%20capital.%20Also%20called%20DJB%2C%20the%20board%20treats%20water%20from%20sources%20such%20as%20Yamuna%20river%20and%20Bhakra%20Dam%20and%20canals%20near%20Delhi.%20It%20is%20also%20responsible%20for%20collecting%20and%20disposing%20sewage%20from%20areas%20under%20New%20Delhi%20Municipal%20Council%20and%20Delhi%20Cantonment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20The%20Case%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20case%20is%20based%20on%20an%20FIR%20registered%20by%20CBI.%20It%20alleges%20that%20DJB's%20former%20chief%20engineer%2C%20Jagdish%20Kumar%20Arora%2C%20had%20awarded%20a%20Rs%2038-crore%20contract%20to%20NKG%20Infrastructure%20Limited.%20This%20contract%20was%20for%20the%20supply%2C%20installation%20and%20testing%20of%20electromagnetic%20flow%20meters.%20The%20FIR%20alleges%20that%20officials%20of%20DJB%20and%20NBCC%20illegally%20favoured%20NKG%20Infrastructure%20for%20a%20bribe.%20The%20ED%20arrested%20Mr%20Arora%20and%20a%20contractor%2C%20Anil%20Kumar%20Aggarwal%2C%20on%20January%2031.%20NKG%20Infrastructure%2C%20it%20is%20alleged%2C%20got%20the%20bid%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20forged%20documents%20and%20that%20Mr%20Arora%20was%20aware%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20company%20did%20not%20meet%20the%20technical%20eligibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20The%20AAP%20Link%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%2C%20which%20is%20investigating%20the%20money%20trail%20in%20the%20case%2C%20has%20alleged%20that%20Mr%20Arora%20received%20a%20bribe%20in%20cash%20and%20in%20bank%20accounts%20after%20the%20contract%20went%20to%20NKG%20Infrastructure.%20This%20money%2C%20it%20has%20alleged%2C%20was%20passed%20on%20to%20various%20parties%2C%20including%20%26quot%3Bpersons%20connected%20with%20AAP%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BBribe%20amounts%20were%20also%20passed%20on%20as%20election%20funds%20to%20AAP%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20ED%20statement%20said.%20This%20is%20the%20second%20case%20in%20which%20the%20central%20agency%20has%20charged%20AAP%20with%20taking%20kickbacks.%20In%20the%20other%20case%20in%20which%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20has%20been%20summoned%2C%20the%20ED%20has%20alleged%20that%20kickbacks%20from%20the%20now-scrapped%20Delhi%20liquor%20excise%20policy%20were%20used%20by%20AAP%20for%20its%20Goa%20polls%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Has%20AAP%20Responded%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAP%20leader%20and%20Delhi%20minister%20Atishi%20has%20said%20%26quot%3Bnobody%20knows%20what%20this%20DJB%20case%20is%20about%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThis%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20backup%20plan%20to%20arrest%20(Arvind)%20Kejriwal%20anyhow%20and%20stop%20him%20from%20campaigning%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20the%20media.%20The%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20asked%20to%20appear%20before%20the%20agency%20on%20Monday%20for%20questioning%20in%20the%20DJB%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710661800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F8ohb75t8_arvind-kejriwal_625x300_16_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-is-delhi-jal-board-case-in-which-arvind-kejriwal-got-fresh-summons-5255270%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20the%20legal%20tussle%20between%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20over%20the%20multiple%20summonses%20in%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20case%2C%20the%20central%20agency%20has%20now%20asked%20the%20AAP%20leader%20to%20appear%20for%20questioning%20in%20another%20case%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-is-delhi-jal-board-case-in-which-arvind-kejriwal-got-fresh-summons-5255270%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-is-delhi-jal-board-case-in-which-arvind-kejriwal-got-fresh-summons-5255270%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-is-delhi-jal-board-case-in-which-arvind-kejriwal-got-fresh-summons-5255270%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Big%20Fat%20Indian%20Wedding%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F17130717%2FGHpnMcXWsAA63hy.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20taxonomy%20of%20traditional%20Indian%20families%2C%20my%20maternal%20grandmother%20Ama%2C%20was%20an%20accidental%20matriarch.%20Ironically%2C%20this%20mother%20of%20nine%20was%20pushed