has%20been%2C%20while%20governments%20and%20corporations%20control%20global%20warming%20with%20technical%20fixes.%20But%20this%20attachment%20to%20a%20desired%20outcome%20without%20evidence%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20possible%20is%20blind%20faith%2C%20not%20hope.%20Indeed%20much%20of%20what%20gets%20called%20hope%20today%20actually%20includes%20beliefs%20held%20%3Cem%3Econtrary%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20evidence.%20These%20are%20fantasies%20or%20delusions%2C%20wishful%20thinking%20or%20wilful%20ignorance.%20All%20such%20false%20hopes%20are%20dangerous.%20They%20lull%20us%20into%20inaction.%20They%20guide%20us%20down%20wrong%20paths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20real%20hope%20is%20essential%20for%20human%20thriving.%20And%20real%20hope%20is%20built%20upon%20the%20possible.%20It%E2%80%99s%20arrived%20at%20by%20facing%20hard%20truths%2C%20understanding%20what%20the%20challenges%20truly%20are%2C%20and%20contemplating%20the%20difficult%20tradeoffs.%20It%20isn%E2%80%99t%20passive%3B%20it%20arises%20through%20engagement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20363px)%2085vw%2C%20363px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11123728%2FIMG_2896.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22363%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11123728%2FIMG_2896.jpg%20874w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11123728%2FIMG_2896-219x300.jpg%20219w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11123728%2FIMG_2896-746x1024.jpg%20746w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696598%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22498%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20I%E2%80%99ve%20shown%20in%20this%20series%2C%20to%20significantly%20slow%20the%20rate%20of%20anthropogenic%20climate%20change%20and%20its%20underlying%20cause%20of%20ecolo