ountry-trump-warns-if-he-loses-us-presidential-elections%2Famp_articleshow%2F108556649.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI'm%20Indebted%20To%20Dhoni%26quot%3B%3A%20India%20Great's%20Humble%20Praise%20For%20Legendary%20Captain%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOverwhelmed%20by%20emotion%20and%20filled%20with%20gratitude%20at%20being%20grandly%20feted%20for%20hitting%20the%20500-wicket%20mark%20in%20Tests%2C%20Ravichandaran%20Ashwin%20on%20Saturday%20recalled%20the%20one%20man%20he%20would%20forever%20be%20%26quot%3Bindebted%20to%26quot%3B%20for%20showing%20faith%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bnobody%26quot%3B%2013%20years%20ago%20--%20his%20first%20IPL%20and%20India%20captain%20Mahendra%20Singh%20Dhoni.%20With%20516%20scalps%20in%20100%20Tests%2C%20Ashwin%20is%20a%20bonafide%20superstar%20in%20Indian%20cricket%2C%20just%20second%20behind%20the%20great%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Anil%20Kumble%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F265-anil-kumble-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAnil%20Kumble%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20list%20of%20top%20Indian%20wicket-takers%20in%20the%20five-day%20format.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20was%20not%20the%20case%20back%20in%202008%20when%20he%20was%20roped%20in%20as%20a%20local%20spinner%20by%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings.%20He%20did%20not%20get%20a%20game%20that%20year%20as%20the%20legendary%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Muttiah%20Muralitharan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F313-muttiah-muralidaran-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMuttiah%20Muralitharan%3C%2Fa%3E%20led%20their%20spin%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhoni%20flung%20the%20new%20ball%20to%20Ashwin%20in%20the%202011%20IPL%20final%20against%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bangalore%20and%20the%20then%20rookie%20off-spinner%20made%20an%20impact%20in%20the%20fourth%20ball%20itself%2C%20dismissing%20an%20in-form%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Chris%20Gayle%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F199-chris-gayle-playerprofile%5C%22%3EChris%20Gayle%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20year%20he%20made%20his%20India%20debut%20under%20Dhoni%2C%20picking%20up%20the%20player%20of%20the%20match%20honours%20in%20the%20game%20against%20the%20West%20Indies%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%202008%20I%20met%20all%20the%20greats%20(in%20CSK%20dressing%20room)%20Mathew%20Hayden%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22MS%20Dhoni%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F700-ms-dhoni-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMS%20Dhoni%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20sat%20through%20(IPL)%202008.%20I%20was%20a%20nobody%20then%2C%20where%20am%20I%20to%20play%20in%20a%20team%20that%20had%20Muttiah%20Muralitharan%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ashwin%2C%20who%20was%20felicitated%20by%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Cricket%20Association%20in%20a%20grand%20ceremony%20for%20his%20rare%20achievements%2C%20in%20a%20dipped-in-emotion%20voice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20indebted%20to%20Dhoni%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20life%20for%20what%20he%20gave%20me.%20He%20gave%20me%20an%20opportunity%20with%20the%20new%20ball%20to%20go%20head%20on%20with%20Chris%20Gayle%20and%2017%20years%20later%20Anil%20bhai%20would%20be%20talking%20about%20the%20same%20episode%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20fondly%20recalled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20magical%20Chepauk%20night%20for%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20was%20just%20a%20beginning%20for%20Ashwin.%20With%20several%20current%20and%20former%20stars%20paying%20tributes%20to%20him%2C%20Ashwin%20understandably%20felt%20overwhelmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20generally%20search%20for%20words%20to%20express%20how%20I%20feel.%20I%20am%20truly%20humbled%20and%20grateful%20to%20be%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20quipped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2037-year-old%20Chennai%20man%20is%20among%20the%20finest%20thinkers%20of%20the%20game%20and%20he%20has%20found%20a%20way%20to%20constantly%20reinvent%20himself%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20bagful%20of%20wickets%20in%20the%20longest%20format.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20described%20himself%20as%20argumentative%20but%20only%20in%20pursuit%20of%20new%20perspectives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnil%20bhai%20and%20Rahul%20(Dravid)%20bhai%20briefly%20mentioned%20that%20it%20is%20very%20tough%20to%20win%20an%20argument%20with%20me.%20It%20is%20true%20because%20I%20believe%20argument%20is%20one%20of%20the%20greatest%20pathways%20to%20excellence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BArgument%20is%20never%20with%20the%20person.%20It%20is%20always%20with%20the%20true%20learning%20that%20comes%20at%20the%20end%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20as%20Kumble%20watched%20on%20from%20the%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshwin%20also%20thanked%20a%20host%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20greats%2C%20who%20were%20in%20attendance%2C%20including%20his%20first%20First-Class%20captain%20S%20Badrinath%20and%20former%20batter%20S%20Sharath%2C%20who%20is%20now%20an%20India%20selector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshwin%2C%20who%20is%20especially%20lethal%20against%20the%20left-handers%2C%20recalled%20how%20Sharath%20helped%20him%20become%20a%20better%20bowler%20against%20the%20southpaws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20spoke%20about%20how%20I%20tormented%20left-handers%20day%20in%20and%20day%20out.%20My%20first%20tryst%20with%20left%20handers%2C%20Mr%20S%20Sharath%20is%20sitting%20in%20the%20front.%20Someone%20told%20me%20if%20you%20are%20that%20good%20an%20off-spinner%20try%20and%20get%20this%20man%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20did%20get%20him%20out%20once%2C%20caught%20at%20slip%20and%20I%20played%20several%20more%20games%20with%20Sharath%2C%20he%20never%20got%20out%20to%20me%20again.%20That's%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20batter%20he%20was.%20I%20bowled%20to%20him%20a%20lot%20and%20hence%20became%20a%20far%20better%20bowler%20to%20the%20left-handers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20is%20Ashwin's%20commitment%20to%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20club%20cricket%20that%20till%20date%20he%20makes%20himself%20available%20for%20domestic%20events%20when%20he%20is%20not%20on%20national%20duty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20place%20has%20given%20me%20so%20much%20that%20I%20want%20to%20keep%20coming%20back%20here.%20People%20keep%20asking%20why%20do%20you%20want%20to%20go%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTomorrow%2C%20I%20might%20not%20be%20alive%20but%20my%20soul%20will%20be%20hanging%20around%20this%20place.%20This%20is%20what%20this%20place%20means%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Ashwin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710644760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fqhpb4r68_ms-dhoni-bcci_625x300_24_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fi-am-indebted-to-ms-dhoni-r-ashwins-humble-praise-for-legendary-captain-ahead-of-ipl-2024-5252500%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22MS%20Dhoni%20is%20among%20the%20great%20captains%20the%20world%20has%20ever%20seen.%20He%20is%20the%20only%20skipper%20to%20win%20all%20three%20major%20ICC%20white-ball%20tournaments.%20Additionally%2C%20Dhoni%20has%20won%20five%20IPL%20titles.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20notorious%20death%20row%20closes%2C%20inmates%20fear%20what%20awaits%20in%20new%20prisons%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710644566000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FB60C%2Fproduction%2F_132940664_gettyimages-1130296485.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68558967%234%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20prison%20is%20being%20remade%20into%20a%20rehabilitation%20centre%20that%20will%20not%20include%20people%20sentenced%20to%20death.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A25%2C%22canonicalUrl