20with%20scenes%20of%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Leo%20Barraclough%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fdont-worry-sari-sari-haragonics-1235943721%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fdont-worry-sari-sari-haragonics-1235943721%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fdont-worry-sari-sari-haragonics-1235943721%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Gujarat%20Links%20Are%20Established%20In%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Constable%20Recruitment%20Exam%20Paper%20Leak%20Fiasco%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24193316%2Fimage-1874.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20leaked%20examination%20paper%20and%20answer%20keys%20in%20the%20police%20recruitment%20examination%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20has%20a%20strong%20Gujarat%20connection.%20The%20paper%20was%20printed%20in%20Gujarat.%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20police%20sources%20confirm%20that%20the%20leak%20happened%20from%20the%20warehouse%20of%20the%20transportation%20company%2C%20Transport%20Corporation%20of%20India%20(TCI)%2C%20which%20is%20headquartered%20in%20Gurugram.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20Special%20Task%20Force%20(STF)%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20has%20confirmed%20that%20the%20paper%20leak%20happened%20from%20Ahmedabad%2C%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20constable%20recruitment%20examination%20was%20held%20on%20February%2017%20and%2018%2C%20with%20two%20shifts%20per%20day.%20Around%2048%20lakh%20candidates%20had%20applied%20for%2060%2C244%20constable%20posts.%20According%20to%20police%2C%20as%20many%20as%20246%20people%20have%20been%20arrested%20so%20far%20for%20%E2%80%98fraudulent%20activities%E2%80%99%20during%20the%20recruitment%20exam.%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Adityanath%20had%20then%20scrapped%20the%20examination%20and%20had%20said%20he%20would%20not%20tolerate%20any%20injustice%20to%20youngsters%20of%20the%20state.%20He%20had%20emphasised%20that%20paper%20leaks%20are%20a%20national%20sin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGujarat%20connection%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20paper%20for%20the%20constable%20recruitment%20was%20printed%20in%20Ahmedabad.%20After%20printing%2C%20the%20papers%20were%20to%20be%20sent%20in%20a%20sealed%20manner%20in%20a%20truck%20to%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20The%20company%20assigned%20this%20task%20was%20TCI%20which%20is%20headquartered%20in%20Gurugram.%20The%20police%20now%20confirm%20that%20two%20staffers%20of%20this%20transportation%20company%20along%20with%20a%20doctor%20broke%20into%20the%20sealed%20truck%2C%20scanned%20the%20examination%20paper%20and%20forwarded%20it%20to%20their%20gang%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20week%20before%20the%20examination%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20this%20doctor%20who%20has%20now%20been%20identified%20as%20Dr%20Shubham%20Mandal%20came%20to%20Gujarat%20on%20February%205%20and%208.%20He%20landed%20at%20the%20Ahmedabad%20airport.%20Two%20transport%20company%20employees%20%E2%80%94%20Shivam%20Giri%20and%20Rohit%20Pandey%20%E2%80%94%20were%20familiar%20with%20the%20warehouse%20and%20their%20company%20truck.%20They%20entered%20the%20warehouse%20and%20identified%20the%20truck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Flakh-aspirants-jobs-exams-constable-recruitment%5C%22%3E48%20Lakh%20Aspirants%20For%2067%2C000%20Jobs%3A%20How%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Conducted%20the%20Constable%20Recruitment%20Exam%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20gang%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20brains%20behind%20this%20were%20Ravi%20Attri%2C%20Abhishek%20Shukla%20and%20Ravi%20Mishra%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20They%20have%20been%20involved%20in%20paper%20leaks%20in%20the%20state%20before%20also.%20They%20were%20reportedly%20in%20touch%20with%201500%20aspirants.%20These%20examination%20aspirants%20were%20taken%20to%20a%20resort%20in%20Manesar%20where%20they%20were%20given%20answer%20keys.%20In%20a%20sophisticated%20manner%2C%20these%20aspirants%20were%20taught%20to%20mug%20up%20the%20answer%20keys.%20Vikram%20Pahal%2C%20a%20constable%20with%20Delhi%20police%20was%20working%20with%20the%20gang.%20He%20has%20also%20been%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20the%20scam%20broke%20out%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20earlier%20maintained%20that%20the%20examination%20paper%20leak%20was%20fake%20news%20that%20had%20begun%20from%20social%20media%2C%20they%20were%20compelled%20to%20take%20cognisance%20and%20take%20action.%20The%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20public%20service%20and%20recruitment%20board%20chairperson%20Renuka%20Mishra%20was%20sacked.%20The%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20had%20to%20do%20this%20after%20screenshots%20of%20the%20leaked%20examination%20paper%20were%20posted%20on%20X%20(formerly%20called%20Twitter).%20The%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20then%20got%20into%20the%20picture.%20Subsequently%2C%20Abhishek%20Mishra%2C%20Shivam%20Giri%20and%20Rohit%20Pandey%20were%20arrested.%20Police%20investigations%20later%20found%20the%20involvement%20of%20Mahendra%20Sharma%20and%20a%20Delhi%20constable%20Vikram%20Pahal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGujarat%E2%80%99s%20dubious%20paper%20leak%20record%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Congress%20leaders%20Manish%20Doshi%20and%20Hiren%20Banker%2C%C2%A0at%20least%2014%20public%20service%20examination%20papers%20have%20been%20leaked%20in%20Gujarat%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years.%20They%20told%20%3Cem%3EVibes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CGujarat%20is%20the%20epicentre%20of%20all%20paper%20leaks%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBanker%20and%20Doshi%20told%20%3Cem%3EVo!%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20following%20examination%20papers%20were%20leaked%20in%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetails%20of%20paper%20leaks%20in%20Gujarat%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E2014%3A%20GPSC%20Chief%20Officer%E2%80%99s%20Paper%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E2015%3A%20Talati%20Paper%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E2016%3A%20Talati%20exam%20paper%20conducted%20by%20District%20Panchayat%20in%20Gandhinagar%2C%20Modasa%2C%20Surendranagar%20district%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E2018%3A%20TAT%20-Teacher%20Paper%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E2018%3A%20Mukhya%20Sevika%20Paper%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E2018%3A%20Nayab%20Chitnis%20Paper%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E2018%3A%20LRD-Lorakrakshak%20Dal%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E2019%3A%20Non-Secretariat%20Clerk%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E2020%3A%20Government%20Recruitment%20Exams%20(Corona%20Era)%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E2021%3A%20Head%20Clerk%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E2021%3A%20DGVCL%20Vidyut%20Asst%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E2021%3A%20Sub%20Auditor%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E2022%3A%20Forest%20Guard%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E2023%3A%20Junior%20Clerk.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGujarat%E2%80%99s%20paper%20leak%20prohibition%20act%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20numerous%20paper%20leaks%20and%20disillusionment%20of%20candidates%20appearing%20for%20various%20government%20examinations%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20government%20in%20Gujarat%20introduced%20the%20Gujarat%20Public%20Examination%20(Prevention%20of%20Unfair%20Methods)%20Bill%2C%202023.%20In%20February%202023%2C%20the%20Gujarat%20assembly%20unanimously%20passed%20a%20bill%20to%20check%20paper%20leak%20in%20government%20recruitment%20examinations%20with%20a%20significant%20modification%20pointed%20out%20by%20then%20senior%20Congress%20legislator%20Arjun%20Modhwadia.%20The%20original%20Bill%20had%20excluded%20school%20and%20college%20examinations%20from%20the%20purview%20of%20the%20Act.%20The%20new%20law%20has%20a%20stipulation%20of%20ten%20years%20of%20imprisonment%20and%20minimum%20one%20crore%20of%20penalty%20for%20those%20involved%20in%20this%20heinous%20act%20of%20leaking%20papers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModhwadia%20joined%20BJP%20this%20month%20to%20work%20under%20the%20dynamic%20vision%20and%20leadership%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fup-police-recruitment-exam-cancelled-bjp-yields-to-pressure-amid-paper-leak-allegations-protests%5C%22%3EUP%20Police%20Recruitment%20Exam%20Cancelled%3A%20BJP%20Yields%20to%20Pressure%20Amid%20Paper%20Leak%20Allegations%2C%20Protests%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20exam%20paper%20leak%20case%20progress%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20arrested%20six%20members%20of%20the%20gang%20from%20Meerut%20on%20March%205%20and%20during%20interrogation%20they%20revealed%20the%20name%20of%20Mahendra%20Sharma%20of%20Dhatrath%20village%20under%20Pillukhera%20police%20station%20of%20Jind%20district%20in%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20joint%20team%20of%20STF%20and%20Kankerkhera%20police%20raided%20a%20place%20in%20Jind%20and%20arrested%20Sharma.%20He%20told%20the%20police%20that%20he%20worked%20in%20a%20shop%20and%20Delhi%20police%20constable%20Vikram%20Pahal%2C%20who%20was%20also%20a%20resident%20of%20his%20village%2C%20approached%20him%20on%20February%2016%20and%20took%20him%20to%20a%20resort%20in%20Gurugram.%20He%20said%20the%20UP%20police%20recruitment%20exam%20paper%20would%20be%20made%20available%20there%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20help%20in%20his%20work%20for%20%E2%82%B92%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahendra%20told%20the%20police%20that%20300%20to%20400%20applicants%20were%20already%20present%20in%20the%20resort%20and%20one%20Gaurav%20Choudhary%20arrived%20there%20along%20with%20more%20applicants.%20He%20had%20a%20meeting%20with%20the%20gathering%20of%20approximately%201500%20applicants.%20Vikram%20Pahal%20was%20present%20at%20the%20resort.%20Young%20boys%20and%20girls%20were%20made%20to%20sit%20in%20a%20row%2C%20offered%20meals%20and%20told%20to%20mug%20up%20the%20answers.%20Each%20candidate%20was%20okay%20to%20pay%20%E2%80%9Cfees%E2%80%9D%20of%20Rs%20seven%20lac%20each.%20The%20gang%20was%20so%20confident%20of%20their%20paper%20leak%20operation%20that%20they%20had%20told%20the%20students%20to%20pay%20seven%20lacs%20after%20the%20examination.%20This%20resort%20paper%20leak%20took%20place%2048%20hours%20before%20the%20government%20examination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vibesofindia.com%2Fgujarat-model-of-paper-leak-rocks-up%2F%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0was%20originally%20published%20on%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vibesofindia.com%2F%5C%22%3EVibes%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710594325000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24193316%2Fimage-1874.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhow-gujarat-links-are-established-in-uttar-pradesh-constable-recruitment-exam-paper-leak-fiasco%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Over%2048%20lakh%20students%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20had%20applied%20for%20over%2060%2C000%20constable%20posts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhow-gujarat-links-are-established-in-uttar-pradesh-constable-recruitment-exam-paper-leak-fiasco%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20excise%20policy%20scam%3A%20K%20Kavitha%20sent%20to%20ED%20custody%20till%20March%2023%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710593631000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-09%2F05%2Ffull%2F1693891857-6121.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fexcise-scam-court-reserves-order-on-ed-s-plea-seeking-kavitha-s-custody-124031600363_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Special%20Judge%20for%20ED%20cases%