he%20need%20for%20policymakers%20to%20involve%20various%20stakeholders%20in%20public%20consultations%20actively.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStartup%20founders%20took%20to%20various%20platforms%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fbusiness%2Fgenai-startups-dont-need-to-seek-govt-nod-before-launch-rajeev-chandrasekhar-9194613%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eshare%20their%20anxieties%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20call%20on%20MeitY%20to%20amend%20or%20repeal%20the%20advisory.%20Without%20diverse%20perspectives%2C%20regulations%20tend%20to%20be%20vague%20and%20confusing%20for%20industries%20and%20result%20in%20an%20extended%20duration%20of%20consultations%20and%20amendments%2C%20delaying%20compliance.%20Moreover%2C%20such%20advisories%20complicate%20the%20process%20of%20compliance%2C%20especially%20for%20the%20startup%20ecosystem.%20Public%20consultations%20need%20to%20be%20the%20starting%20point%20of%20the%20policy-making%20process%2C%20and%20not%20an%20afterthought.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20two-page%20AI%20advisory%20issued%20on%20March%201%2C%20which%20is%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20Word%20document%2C%20and%20has%20not%20been%20announced%20via%20an%20official%20press%20release%20yet%2C%20was%20circulated%20across%20various%20communication%20channels%20before%20it%20was%20confirmed%20by%20news%20articles.%20The%20preceding%20advisories%20merely%20emphasised%20existing%20clauses%20within%20the%20IT%20Act%20and%20Rules%20to%20help%20curb%20the%20spread%20of%20deep-fakes.%20However%2C%20the%20latest%20advisory%20comprises%20of%20vague%20clauses%20and%20terms%20aimed%20at%20regulating%20%E2%80%9CAI%20model(s)%2FLLM%2FGenerative%20AI%2C%20software(s)%20or%20algorithm(s)%E2%80%9D%20without%20processes%20for%20compliance%20and%2C%20hence%2C%20has%20created%20confusion%20in%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Clause%202(c)%20of%20the%20advisory%20asks%20%E2%80%9Call%20intermediaries%2Fplatforms%E2%80%9D%20to%20seek%20government%20approval%20before%20deploying%20%E2%80%9Cunder-testing%2Funreliable%E2%80%9D%20AI%20models%2C%20software%2C%20and%20algorithms%20on%20Indian%20users.%20But%2C%20what%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cplatform%E2%80%9D%3F%20Which%20regulatory%20body%20%E2%80%9Capproves%E2%80%9D%20models%3F%20What%20is%20the%20evaluation%20process%3F%20What%20is%20an%20unreliable%20model%3F%20No%20one%20knows.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20advisory%20was%20immediately%20interpreted%2C%20and%20rightfully%20so%2C%20as%20a%20return%20to%20%E2%80%98license%20%3Cem%3Eraj%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20by%20asking%20presumably%20everyone%20to%20seek%20government%20approval%20on%20their%20models.%20From%20the%20previously%20hands-off%20approach%20to%20AI%20regulation%2C%20this%20advisory%20is%20a%20step%20to%20the%20other%20extreme%20of%20over-regulation.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFollowing%20the%20backlash%20from%20the%20tech%20industry%2C%20m%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Einister%20of%20state%2C%20MeitY%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRajeev_GoI%2Fstatus%2F1764534565715300592%5C%22%3E%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%20posted%20a%20clarification%20on%20X%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fa%3E(previously%20called%20Twitter).%20He%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Estated%20that%20the%20advisory%20is%20only%20for%20%E2%80%9Csignificant%20platforms%E2%80%9D%20and%20will%20not%20apply%20to%20startups.%20However%2C%20the%20advisory%20has%20not%20been%20updated%20to%20reflect%20these%20clarifications%2C%20thereby%20putting%20the%20two%20at%20odds.%20Why%20are%20clarifications%20to%20official%20advisories%20being%20made%20on%20social%20media%3F%20What%20are%20the%20criteria%20for%20being%20significant%3F%20Again%2C%20no%20one%20knows.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20further%20discrepancies%20and%20vagueness%20in%20the%20advisory.%20Clause%202(b)%20requires%20that%20intermediaries%20and%20platforms%20%E2%80%9Cdo%20not%20permit%20any%20bias%20or%20discrimination%20or%20threaten%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20electoral%20process%E2%80%9D.%20However%2C%20as%20per%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.proofnews.org%2Fseeking-election-information-dont-trust-ai%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eresearch%20conducted%20by%20AI%20Democracy%20Projects%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20current%20AI%20models%20do%20not%20accurately%20respond%20to%20prompts%20regarding%20elections%20approximately%2050%25%20of%20the%20time.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20models%20tested%20included%20Anthropic%E2%80%99s%20Claude%2C%20Google%E2%80%99s%20Gemini%2C%20OpenAI%E2%80%99s%20GPT-4%2C%20Meta%E2%80%99s%20Llama%202%20and%20Mistral%E2%80%99s%20Mixtral.%20Considering%20they%20do%20not%20fully%20comply%20with%20the%20advisory%20and%20likely%20fall%20under%20the%20ambit%20of%20%E2%80%9Csignificant%20platforms%E2%80%9D%2C%20this%20raises%20the%20question%20regarding%20penal%20consequences.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fadvisory-on-regulation-of-ai-platforms-needs-to-be-understood-it-ministry-124030400335_1.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20while%20the%20advisory%20is%20not%20legally%20binding%2C%20it%20indicates%20the%20future%20of%20AI%20regulations%20in%20India.%20The%20advisory%20also%20states%20that%20non-compliance%20with%20IT%20Rules%20and%20Act%20provisions%20would%20result%20in%20penalties.%20As%20some%20of%20the%20content%20generated%20by%20such%20AI%20tools%20violates%20provisions%20of%20harmful%20content%20under%20said%20regulations%2C%20will%20all%20these%20platforms%20be%20penalized%3F%20This%20again%20begs%20the%20questions%20regarding%20the%20vague%20definitions%20of%20%E2%80%9Cintermediaries%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cplatforms%E2%80%9D%20and%20whether%20these%20tools%20fall%20under%20these%20categories.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20move%20to%20rein%20in%20the%20AI%20industry%20to%20ensure%20the%20safe%20and%20ethical%20development%20of%20tools%20is%20welcome%2C%20but%20this%20advisory%20and%20the%20precedent%20it%20sets%20for%20future%20regulations%20is%20counterproductive.%20Overarching%20and%20vague%20regulations%20with%20heavy%20penalties%20for%20non-compliance%20would%20disincentivise%20companies%20and%20individuals%20to%20build%20their%20own%20AI%20tools%20and%20innovate.%20Developing%20regulations%20to%20balance%20the%20drive%20to%20innovate%20and%20the%20need%20for%20responsible%20technology%20requires%20open%20conversations%20with%20diverse%20stakeholder%20groups%20such%20as%20developers%2C%20lawyers%2C%20social%20scientists%2C%20doctors%2C%20teachers%2C%20etc.%20from%20diverse%20socio-economic%20backgrounds.%20There%20already%20exist%20multiple%20such%20communities%20and%20fora%20that%20can%20be%20leveraged%20for%20the%20same.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgoogle-search-modi-govt-now-says-ai-advisory-only-advisory-not-regulatory-framework%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Search%3A%20Modi%20Govt%20Now%20Says%20AI%20%E2%80%98Advisory%E2%80%99%20Only%20Advisory%2C%20Not%20Regulatory%20Framework%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3Cins%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20regulatory%20requirements%20to%20ensure%20responsible%20AI%20differs%20depending%20on%20the%20type%20of%20tool%20and%20the%20domain%20within%20which%20it%20is%20being%20deployed.%20This%20follows%20from%20the%20risk-based%20approach%20adopted%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdata.consilium.europa.eu%2Fdoc%2Fdocument%2FST-5662-2024-INIT%2Fen%2Fpdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EEU%20AI%20Act%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20as%20well%20as%20frameworks%20for%20safety-based%20software%20verification%20and%20validation%20globally%20(such%20as%20DO178B%2FC).%20The%20regulations%20that%20would%20apply%20to%20high-risk%20tools%20such%20as%20those%20used%20in%20healthcare%20would%20not%20be%20relevant%20to%20a%20chatbot%20like%20ChatGPT.%20Similarly%2C%20healthcare%20tools%20and%20fintech%20tools%20have%20different%20risks%20and%20requirements.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAI%20regulations%20that%20are%20to%20be%20applied%20across%20the%20industry%20should%20specify%20a%20minimum%20standard%20of%20safety%20that%20must%20be%20met%2C%20rather%20than%20overregulating%20emerging%20technologies.%20For%20higher%20levels%20of%20risk%2C%20additional%20regulations%20and%20guardrails%20specific%20to%20these%20risks%20can%20be%20put%20in%20place%20throughout%20the%20development%20lifecycle.%20Compliance%20and%20regulations%20are%20often%20viewed%20through%20the%20lens%20of%20penalties%20and%20legalese%2C%20but%20should%20instead%20be%20a%20means%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20companies%20can%20comply%20with%20ease%20and%20develop%20safe%20technologies.%20To%20do%20so%2C%20checklists%20to%20gauge%20compliance%20and%20continuous%20policy%20engagements%20with%20the%20ecosystem%20are%20required.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EApart%20from%20legal%20and%20compliance-related%20issues%2C%20there%20are%20a%20multitude%20of%20technical%20concerns%20regarding%20this%20advisory.%20It%20lacks%20details%20on%20the%20application%20process%20for%20approval%20from%20the%20government%2C%20transparency%20in%20reporting%20the%20result%20of%20the%20same%2C%20methods%20for%20testing%20the%20reliability%20and%20%E2%80%9Charmlessness%E2%80%9D%20of%20models%2C%20and%20the%2015-day%20deadline%20for%20reporting%20compliance%20is%20highly%20inadequate%2C%20especially%20when%20no%20one%20knows%20how%20to%20comply.%20Without%20clarity%20and%20amendments%20on%20these%20aspects%2C%20the%20advisory%20cannot%20be%20effectively%20implemented.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20industry%E2%80%99s%20backlash%20due%20to%20this%20advisory%20outlines%20the%20need%20for%20policymakers%20to%20include%20the%20broader%20tech%20industry%20in%20the%20policy-making%20process%20and%20vice%20versa.%20Developers%20and%20designers%20too%20need%20to%20be%20aware%20of%20and%20actively%20engage%20in%20consultations%20that%20are%20carried%20out.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20positive%20outcome%20of%20this%20advisory%20has%20been%20the%20awareness%20raised%20around%20the%20tech%20policy%20regime%20among%20AI%20developers%20and%20startups.%20This%20momentum%20can%20be%20used%20to%20draft%20effective%20regulations%20through%20multi-stakeholder%20consultations%20and%20comments%20from%20the%20industry%20to%20promote%20trust%2C%20safety%2C%20and%20responsible%20technology.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20process%20of%20regulations%20and%20involvement%20of%20regulatory%20bodies%20is%20a%20continuous%20and%20iterative%20process%20during%20any%20technological%20development%20that%20has%20a%20large%20impact%20on%20society.%20Regulations%20cannot%20be%20formulated%20and%20implemented%20in%20haste%20and%20also%20cannot%20be%20an%20afterthought.%20Further%2C%20the%20process%20of%20regulations%20and%20verification%20of%20compliance%20should%20evolve%20to%20include%20diverse%20stakeholders%20to%20ease%20the%20formulation%20of%20effective%20and%20widely%20accepted%20regulations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fanwesha-sen-aa7577189%2F%5C%22%3EAnwesha%20Sen%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20researcher%20and%20community%20organiser%2C%20associated%20with%20Hasgeek.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710592203000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26180001%2Fimage-1169.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Findias-ai-advisory-vague-clauses-and-terms-dont-help-anyone%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Regulations%20cannot%20be%20formulated%20and%20implemented