y%20passes%20without%20a%20strip%20ad%20above%20the%20masthead%20offering%20%E2%80%98Modi%20Sarkar%20ki%20Guarantee%E2%80%99%2C%20assuring%20the%20reader%20of%20everything%20from%20food%2C%20education%20and%20jobs.%20As%20if%20this%20was%20not%20enough%2C%20full%20page%20advertisements%20from%20state%20governments%20(and%20private%20sector%20companies)%20inform%20us%20that%20everything%20they%20do%20and%20hope%20to%20achieve%20is%20because%20of%20the%20munificence%20and%20blessing%20of%20their%20Supreme%20Leader%20%E2%80%93%20his%20face%20prominently%20displayed%20on%20top%20ensures%20that%20we%20get%20the%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20a%20typical%20day%20%E2%80%93%20on%20March%2013%2C%20the%20Bombay%20edition%20of%20the%3Cem%3E%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20a%20full%20page%20ad%20by%20the%20Tata%20group%20welcoming%20Modi%20to%20lay%20the%20%E2%80%98virtual%20stone%20laying%E2%80%99%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20Semiconductor%20Fab%20in%20Dholera%2C%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETurn%20the%20pages%20and%20we%20are%20informed%20that%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20government%20is%20delivering%20on%20%E2%80%98Modi%20ki%20Guarantee%E2%80%99%20for%20a%20%E2%80%98Visit%20to%20Chhattisgarh%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20his%20photo%20looms%20over%20the%20ad%20which%20tells%20us%20of%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98vision%E2%80%99%20for%20development%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20on%20two%20full%20pages%20by%20the%20UP%20government%20%E2%80%93%20again%20with%20Modi%20standing%20next%20too%20(but%20taller%20than)%20chief%20minister%20Adityanath%20hailing%20the%20%E2%80%98magnificent%E2%80%99%C2%A0%20infrastructure%20development%20and%20%E2%80%98cultural%2C%20spiritual%20and%20religious%20renaissance%E2%80%99.%20If%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20what%20this%20means%2C%20the%20ad%20spells%20it%20out%20in%20great%20detail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20comes%20another%20Modi%20guarantee%20of%20World%20Class%20Dedicated%20Freight%20Cor