0with%20world%20leaders%20as%20an%20equal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20different%20this%20time%20round%20is%20the%20concentrated%20focus%20on%20the%20performance%20and%20promises%20of%20the%20Modi%20sarkar%2C%20without%20any%20reference%20to%20the%20disasters%20of%20these%20past%2010%20years%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbanking%2Faakar-patel-reserve-bank-of-india-demonetisation%5C%22%3Edemonetisation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fqz.com%2Fhow-china-has-been-nibbling-away-at-indian-territory-1850297445%5C%22%3Etakeover%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Indian%20land%20by%20China.%20That%20is%20what%20parties%20do%20when%20elections%20are%20coming%2C%20but%20not%20in%20such%20a%20concentrated%20manner%20and%20not%20by%20using%20public%20funds.%20Fully%20aware%20that%20the%20situation%20on%20the%20ground%20may%20not%20be%20as%20rosy%20as%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20his%20ministers%20talk%20about%2C%20the%20campaign%20is%20full%20of%20grand%20claims%20and%20assurances.%20A%20word%20to%20the%20copy%20writer%20though%20%E2%80%93%20A%20headline%20like%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Vanchiton%20ki%20Varivata%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20wasted%20in%20an%20English%20newspaper%2C%20and%20perhaps%20even%20in%20a%20Hindi%20one%2C%20but%20that%20is%20how%20the%20Sangh%20thinks%20and%20speaks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20is%20taking%20no%20chances%20%E2%80%93%20it%20has%20broken%20up%20with%20old%20allies%20and%20aligned%20with%20those%20it%20called%20corrupt%20%E2%80%93%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Ajit%20Pawar%20in%20Maharashtra.%20It%20has%20worked%20to%20break%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20%E2%80%93%20in%20Bihar%2C%20for%20instance.%20It%20has%20let%20loose%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fed-cbi-devious-track-record%5C%22%3Eenforcement%20agencies%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20fully%20aware%20that%20it%20now%20needs%20seats%20from%20beyond%20the%20states%20that%20usually%20support%20it%20%E2%80%93%20UP%2C%20Gujarat%20and%20the%20Hindi-speaking%20belt%20%E2%80%93%20it%20is%20doing%20everything%20to%20ensure%20that%20it%20remains%20on%20the%20top%20of%20the%20voters%E2%80%99%20mind%20on%20a%20daily%20basis.%20Modi%20is%20the%20biggest%20draw%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%2C%20so%20it%E2%80%99s%20natural%20that%20he%20is%20projected%20the%20most%20by%20way%20of%20these%20daily%20ads%2C%20even%20if%20it%20means%20our%20tax%20money%20has%20to%20pay%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20sarkar%20is%20a%20conceited%20way%20of%20suggesting%20that%20it%20is%20%E2%80%98his%E2%80%99%20government%20%E2%80%93%20the%20concept%20of%20the%20collective%20just%20does%20not%20exist%20in%20the%20BJP%20as%20of%20today%2C%20once%20proud%20of%20being%20a%20collegial%20party%2C%20where%20no%20one%20person%20was%20above%20the%20other.%20Now%20it%20is%20Modi%2C%20Modi%20and%20more%20Modi%2C%20but%20only%20up%20to%20a%20point%20%E2%80%93%20all%20successes%20are%20his%2C%20all%20failures%20are%20because%20of%20someone%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20at%20all%20the%20party%20and%20its%20allies%20do%20not%20get%20the%20400%20seats%2C%20370%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20that%20it%20is%20aiming%20for%20%E2%80%93%20apparently%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-mp-says-partys-400-seat-goal-for-2024-is-so-it-can-change-constitution%5C%22%3Echange%20the%20constitution%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20an%20MP%20from%20Karnataka%20has%20helpfully%20informed%20us%20%E2%80%93%20who%20will%20get%20the%20blame%3F%20This%20is%20not%20just%20pre-election%20rhetoric%2C%20Modi%20genuinely%20wants%20to%20break%20previous%20records.%20But%20it%E2%80%99s%20an%20ambitious%20target%20to%20reach%3B%20in%20fact%20303%2C%20the%20number%20of%20seats%20it%20won%20the%20last%20time%2C%20also%20looks%20difficult.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20big%20promises%20%E2%80%93%20removing%20Article%20370%2C%20a%20temple%20at%20Ayodhya%2C%20the%20Citizenship%2