nduct%20the%20enquiry%20in%2015%20days%20and%20submit%20the%20report%20to%20the%20CWW.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CWW%20of%20the%20recipient%20state%20would%20share%20the%20report%20with%20his%20counterpart%20in%20the%20donor%20state.%20The%20donor%20state%20CWW%20would%20be%20taking%20a%20final%20decision%20on%20transfer%20to%20be%20accepted%20or%20rejected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fcaptive-elephant-transfer-rules-notified-101710528460183.html%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20reported%20that%20the%20transfer%2C%20according%20to%20the%20new%20rules%2C%20would%20be%20permitted%20if%20the%20donor%20is%20no%20longer%20capable%20of%20taking%20care%20of%20the%20captive%20elephant.%20For%20a%20transfer%20to%20be%20allowed%2C%20the%20genetic%20profile%20of%20the%20elephant%20has%20to%20be%20entered%20into%20an%20MoEFCC%20application%2C%20electronically.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710590402000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F17145331%2FAsian-elephant.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fgovt-notifies-captive-elephant-transfer-rules%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20transfer%2C%20according%20to%20the%20new%20rules%2C%20would%20be%20permitted%20if%20the%20donor%20is%20no%20longer%20capable%20of%20taking%20care%20of%20the%20captive%20elephant.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fgovt-notifies-captive-elephant-transfer-rules%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lok%20Sabha%20elections%202024%20Phase%20I%3A%20Voting%20on%20April%2019%3B%20check%20details%20here%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710588858000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fassets%2Fweb-assets%2Fimages%2FBusiness_Standard_685x385.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Felections%2Flok-sabha-election%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-phase-i-voting-on-april-19-details-here-124031600470_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lok%20Sabha%20polls%202024%3A%2021%20states%20and%20Union%20territories%20will%20go%20to%20polls%20in%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20the%202024%20general%20elections%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Felections%2Flok-sabha-election%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-phase-i-voting-on-april-19-details-here-124031600470_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Felections%2Flok-sabha-election%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-phase-i-voting-on-april-19-details-here-124031600470_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Felections%2Flok-sabha-election%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-phase-i-voting-on-april-19-details-here-124031600470_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20Eve%20of%20Election%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20Enhances%20Quota%20of%20Politically%20Influential%20Paharis%2C%20Expands%20OBC%20List%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F16163329%2FUntitled-design-49.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESrinagar%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Less%20than%2024%20hours%20before%20the%20imposition%20of%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20(MCC)%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20the%20administration%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20on%20Friday%20evening%20announced%20amendments%20to%20the%20Union%20territory%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20rules%20to%20enhance%20the%20quota%20of%20politically%20influential%20Pahari%20community%20and%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%2C%20apart%20from%20the%20addition%20of%2015%20more%20communities%20in%20the%20latter%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20parties%20have%20alleged%20that%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20move%20shows%20that%20the%20BJP%20wants%20to%20derive%20electoral%20mileage%20from%20it%20in%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReservation%20for%20Paharis%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UT%E2%80%99s%20administrative%20council%20headed%20by%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20Manoj%20Sinha%20cleared%20a%20proposal%20to%20grant%2010%25%20reservation%20to%20Pahari%20ethnic%20tribe%2C%20Paddari%20tribe%2C%20Kolis%20and%20Gadda%20Brahmin%20communities.%20The%20quota%20of%20these%20communities%20was%20announced%20two%20months%20after%20the%20parliament%20passed%20a%20bill%20to%20declare%20them%20as%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20and%20just%20a%20day%20before%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20announced%20the%20schedule%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20being%20cleared%20by%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20respectively%20on%20February%206%20and%209%2C%20the%20President%20of%20India%20gave%20assent%20to%20the%20bill%20on%20February%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20four%20communities%20notified%20as%20STs%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20the%20politically%20significant%20Pahari%20community%20was%20entitled%20to%204%25%20reservation%20from%202019%20onwards%20after%20the%20then%20Governor%20Satya%20Pal%20Malik%20gave%20assent%20to%20a%20bill%20granting%20them%20reservation%20in%20jobs%20and%20admissions%20in%20government-run%20professional%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20grant%20of%20ST%20status%20to%20Paharis%20evoked%20widespread%20resentment%20from%20Gujjar-Bakerwal%20communities%2C%20who%20alleged%20that%20the%20move%20was%20aimed%20at%20diluting%20their%20tribal%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bid%20to%20pacify%20the%20Gujjar-Bakerwal%20communities%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20LG-led%20administration%20have%20repeatedly%20maintained%20from%2020222%20that%20their%20quota%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20affected%20by%20the%20grant%20of%20reservation%20to%20Paharis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20balancing%20act%20between%20the%20two%20communities%2C%20both%20Paharis%20and%20three%20other%20communities%20declared%20as%20STs%20this%20year%20and%20STs%20notified%20earlier%20would%20now%20get%2010%25%20reservation%20each%2C%20taking%20reservation%20of%20ST%20category%20to%2020%25%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20grant%20of%20ST%20status%20to%20Paharis%20and%20enhancement%20of%20their%20quota%20is%20part%20of%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janta%20Party%E2%80%99s%20ambitious%20plan%20to%20woo%20the%20Pahari%20community%2C%20which%20is%20in%20majority%20in%20seven%20out%20of%20eight%20segments%20of%20the%20Pir%20Panchal%20region%2C%20comprising%20Muslim-majority%20Rajouri%20and%20Poonch%20districts.%20Of%20these%20seven%20segments%2C%20six%20are%20part%20of%20the%20Anantnag-Rajouri%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20is%20likely%20to%20benefit%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20Anantnag-Rajouri%20Lok%20Sabha%20segment%2C%20which%20is%20the%20first-ever%20electoral%20unit%20that%20transcends%20the%20geographical%20boundaries%20of%20Kashmir%20and%20Jammu%20region.%20This%20seat%20comprising%2018%20assembly%20segments%20%E2%80%93%20seven%20of%20Jammu%20and%2011%20of%20Kashmir%20%E2%80%93%20is%20partly%20riddled%20with%20caste%20faultlines%20and%20partly%20witnessed%20low%20turnout%20in%20elections%20after%201987%20polls%20which%20were%20rigged%20and%20believed%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20main%20causes%20behind%20armed%20militancy%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20carving%20out%20of%20the%20seat%20by%20the%20delimitation%20commission%20was%20dubbed%20as%20a%20brazen%20instance%20of%20%E2%80%9Cgerrymandering%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Celectoral%20manipulation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20groups%20and%20enhancement%20of%20OBC%20quota%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20administrative%20council%20has%20also%20added%2015%20more%20communities%20to%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%2C%20besides%20enhancing%20their%20quota%20to%208%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20classes%20being%20added%20to%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20OBC%20list%20include%20Waghey%20(Chopan)%2C%20Ghirath%2FBhati%2FChang%20community%2C%20Jat%20community%2C%20Saini%20community%2C%20Markabans%2FPonywalas%2C%20Sochi%20community%2C%20Christian%20Biradari%20(converted%20from%20Hindu%20Valmiki)%2C%20Sunar%2FSwarankar%20Teeli%20(Hindu%20Teeli%20along%20with%20already%20existing%20Muslim%20Teli)%2C%20Perna%2FKouro(Kaurav)%2C%20Bojru%2FDecount%2FDubdabay%20Brahmin%2C%20Gorkans%2C%20Gorkhas%2C%20West%20Pakistani%20refugees%20(excluding%20SCs)%20and%20Acharyas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20recognising%20new%20social%20groups%2C%20the%20government%20also%20enhanced%20the%20quota%20of%20OBCs%20to%208%25%20from%204%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20amendment%20in%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Reservation%20Act%20in%20December%202023%2C%20the%20OBCs%20were%20known%20as%20%E2%80%9Cweak%20and%20underprivileged%20classes%20(social%20castes)%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20UT.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20declaration%20of%20these%20communities%20as%20OBCs%20and%20enhancement%20of%20their%20quota%20would%20strengthen%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20grip%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Udhampur%20seats%2C%20which%20the%20party%20had%20won%20consecutively%20in%20the%202014%20and%202019%20LS%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETiming%20shows%20electoral%20motives%20behind%20the%20move%3A%20Opposition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20four-time%20MLA%20and%20senior%20CPI%20(M)%20leader%20MY%20Tarigami%20attributed%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20motives%20behind%20the%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20for%20the%20election%20purposes%20and%20that%20is%20why%20the%20announcement%20has%20been%20made%20a%20day%20before%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20spokesperson%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20unit%20of%20Congress%2C%20Ravinder%20Sharma%20said%20the%20timing%20of%20these%20amendments%20shows%20that%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20wants%20to%20derive%20electoral%20mileage%20from%20the%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20should%20have%20announced%20the%20quota%20for%20Paharis%20and%20other%20communities%20immediately%20after%20the%20President%20of%20India%20gave%20assent%20to%20the%20bill%20granting%20ST%20status%20to%20them%2C%20but%20they%20delayed%20it%20due%20to%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710588558000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F16163329%2FUntitled-design-49.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fon-eve-of-election-jk-enhances-quota-of-politically-influential-paharis-expands-obc-list%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20administrative%20council%20headed%20by%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20Manoj%20Sinha%20cleared%20a%20proposal%20to%20grant%2010%25%20reservation%20to%20Pahari%20ethnic%20tribe%2C%20Paddari%20tribe%2C%20Kolis%20and%20Gadda%20Brahmin%20communities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fon-eve-of-election-jk-enhances-quota-of-politically-influential-paharis-expands-obc-list%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22New%20India%20election%20to%20be%20held%20in%20seven%20stages%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710588149000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F17248%2Fproduction%2F_132929749_gettyimages-1819251668-594x594.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-68573277%231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20seeking%20a%20rare%20third%20term%20in%20the%20vote%20beginning%20in%20April.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A25%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-68573277%22%2C%22cdnAmpU