dard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fzeel-shareholders-approve-appointment-of-three-independent-directors-124031600336_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Zee%20Entertainment%20Enterprises%20shareholders%20have%20approved%20the%20appointment%20of%20three%20independent%20directors%20to%20the%20company's%20board.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fzeel-shareholders-approve-appointment-of-three-independent-directors-124031600336_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fzeel-shareholders-approve-appointment-of-three-independent-directors-124031600336_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fzeel-shareholders-approve-appointment-of-three-independent-directors-124031600336_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20It%20Takes%20To%20Be%20The%20Keeper%20of%20A%20City%E2%80%99s%20Lore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F16161042%2FScreen-Shot-2024-03-16-at-4.10.16-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20was%20preparing%20for%20my%20research%20visit%20to%20Indore%20for%20a%20study%20on%20the%20princely%20state%20of%20Indore%2C%20all%20I%20found%20online%20were%20a%20few%20articles%20from%20%3Cem%3EFree%20Press%20Journal%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20the%20city.%20It%20was%20just%20a%20glimpse%20of%20how%20much%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98national%E2%80%99%20media%20coverage%20and%20public%20history%20writing%20is%20focussed%20on%20the%20metropolitan%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbsence%2C%20inaccessibility%2C%20decay%20of%20archives%20and%20historical%20artefacts%20are%20constant%20challenges%20faced%20by%20history%20scholars%20in%20India.%20The%20lack%20of%20historical%20consciousness%2C%20poor%20funding%2C%20disinterest%2C%20discrimination%2C%20and%20destruction%20of%20the%20archives%20based%20on%20the%20ideology%20of%20the%20ruling%20disposition%20are%20some%20of%20the%20known%20reasons%20why%20such%20problems%20exist.%20These%20challenges%20are%20acute%20as%20one%20moves%20beyond%20the%20metropolitan%20cities%2C%20into%20the%20smaller%20cities%20and%20towns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHistory%20in%20India%2C%20has%20mostly%20been%20studied%20from%20the%20perspective%20of%20the%20nation%20and%20to%20such%20endeavour%20small%20places%20are%20often%20insignificant.%20Also%20due%20to%20the%20policy%20of%20housing%20all%20the%20state%20archives%20in%20capital%20cities%20and%20the%20absence%20of%20efforts%20to%20do%20neighbourhood%20or%20local%2Fregional%20histories%2C%20smaller%20cities%20almost%20feel%20%E2%80%98history%20less.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20inspite%20of%20the%20institutional%20gap%2C%20voices%20from%20the%20smaller%20cities%20are%20not%20silent.%20Each%20time%20I%20have%20ventured%20into%20these%20cities%20in%20search%20of%20archives%2C%20I%20have%20always%20met%20individuals%20who%20have%20taken%20upon%20themselves%20the%20task%20of%20archiving%2C%20preserving%2C%20narrating%2C%20and%20circulating%20historical%20narratives%20%E2%80%94%20all%20for%20the%20love%20of%20the%20place%20and%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndore-based%20Zafar%20Ansari%20is%20one%20such%20person%20who%20has%20been%20painstakingly%20collecting%20historical%20artefacts%20on%20Indore%20since%20three%20decades.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20all%20started%20when%20I%20received%20the%20National%20Youth%20Award%20for%20my%20social%20activities%20in%201994.%20The%20then%20President%20Dr%20Shankar%20Dayal%20Sharma%20said%2C%20do%20something%20great%2C%20and%20then%20I%20decided%20I%20will%20build%20a%20museum%20for%20Indore%2C%E2%80%9DAnsari%20says%20with%20a%20sparkle%20in%20his%20eye%20as%20he%20narrated%20his%20dream%20to%20make%20a%20museum%20for%20his%20beloved%20city%20Indore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20will%20be%20one%20of%20its%20kind%20museum%2C%20dedicated%20to%20the%20city%2C%20telling%20the%20story%20of%20the%20city%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20mentioned.%20His%20office%20in%20Barwani%20Plaza%20in%20Old%20Palasia%2C%20bustling%20with%20artefacts%2C%20feels%20like%20a%20portal%20into%20another%20time.%20As%20one%20spends%20time%20with%20these%20objects%2C%20they%20start%20speaking%20through%20the%20voice%20of%20Ansari.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20miniature%20maker%20for%20industries%20by%20profession%2C%20Ansari%20spends%20more%20than%2060%25%20of%20his%20income%20towards%20the%20museum.%20He%20never%20lets%20any%20historical%20object%20pertaining%20to%20Indore%20pass%2C%20without%20acquiring%20it%2C%20sometimes%20this%20means%20he%20has%20had%20to%20pay%20very%20high%20price.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20almost%20like%20an%20addiction%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20its%20flip%20sides.%20I%20have%20never%20been%20able%20to%20pay%20my%20daughter%E2%80%99s%20education%20fee%20before%20the%20last%20date.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20history%20walks%2C%20myth-busting%20artefacts%20and%20rare%20photographs%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnsari%20is%20also%20committed%20towards%20sharing%20his%20collection.%20He%20conducts%20history%20walks%20in%20the%20city%20and%20curates%20specific%20objects%20from%20his%20collection%20to%20tell%20stories%20of%20the%20city.%20Ansari%20has%20recently%20conducted%20one%20such%20walk%20for%20some%20of%20the%20dignitaries%20who%20had%20visited%20India%20during%20the%20G20%20summit.%20He%20regularly%20runs%20a%20history%20column%20in%20%3Cem%3EDainik%20Bhaskar%3C%2Fem%3E%20where%20he%20reintroduces%20stories%20of%20the%20past%20to%20Indore%E2%80%99s%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20just%20write%20about%20Kings%2C%20but%20also%20about%20common%20people%2C%20their%20lives%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20what%20a%20historian%20would%20call%20the%20social%20history%20of%20the%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fart-architecture-design-biennale-government-support-politicisation%5C%22%3EArt%2C%20Architecture%20and%20Design%20Biennale%3A%20The%20Fine%20Line%20Between%20Government%20Support%20and%20Politicisation%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20his%20consistent%20effort%20of%20writing%20more%20than%20300%20essays%20on%20history%2C%20Ansari%20has%20built%20a%20cannon%20of%20public%20history%20for%20Indore.%20Sitting%20among%20those%20objects%2C%20he%20narrated%20how%20Indore%20(state)%20became%20a%20commercial%20centre%20due%20to%20its%20close%20connection%20with%20opium%20trade%2C%20%E2%80%9COpium%20would%20come%20from%20Mansur%20to%20Indore%20and%20then%20to%20Bombay.%20Many%20traders%20and%20merchants%20from%20Rajputana%20and%20Gujarat%20settled%20here%20to%20do%20opium%20trade%20with%20China.%20After%20the%20ban%20on%20opium%2C%20the%20trade%20was%20converted%20to%20cotton%20industry.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnsari%20is%20hopeful%20that%20his%20museum%20will%20be%20a%20pedagogic%20intervention.%20%E2%80%9CHistory%20is%20not%20something%20to%20be%20taught%20in%20a%20classroom%2C%20it%20has%20to%20be%20taught%20in%20an%20archive%20or%20a%20monument%20or%20on%20field%20using%20objects%20and%20artefacts%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%20His%20work%20with%20the%20artefacts%20also%20helps%20him%20dispel%20certain%20myths%20and%20false%20narratives%20in%20circulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnsari%E2%80%99s%20collection%20has%20helped%20writers%20like%20Geraldin%20Lenain%20to%20write%20books%20such%20as%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Last%20Maharaja%20of%20Indore%3C%2Fem%3E%20by%20providing%20access%20to%20many%20rare%20photographs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20historian%20or%20an%20antiquarian%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20meeting%20Ansari%2C%20I%20was%20wondering%2C%20if%20there%20is%20a%20term%20to%20describe%20this%20love%20for%20history%2C%20something%20like%20a%20cinephile%20in%20case%20of%20film.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20historian%20is%20often%20a%20tag%20used%20to%20describe%20someone%20who%20engages%20in%20the%20work%20associated%20with%20history%20making%2C%20professionally%2C%20i.e.%20as%20a%20main%20vocation.%20A%20history%20buff%2C%20focusses%20more%20on%20consumption%20of%20history%20and%20fails%20to%20capture%20the%20commitment%20shown%20by%20these%20keepers%20of%20a%20city%E2%80%99s%20lore.%20A%20collector%2C%20is%20often%20differentiated%20from%20an%20archivist%20as%20someone%20who%20is%20more%20involved%20in%20the%20process%20of%20acquiring%20artefacts%2C%20and%20is%20not%20primarily%20oriented%20towards%20providing%20access.%20Someone%20like%20Ansari%2C%20however%2C%20who%20harbours%20a%20hope%20to%20build%20a%20museum%2C%20would%20fall%20somewhere%20in%20between%20these%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECambridge%20Dictionary%20offers%20a%20word%20antiquarian%2C%20%E2%80%9Ca%20person%20who%20studies%20or%20collects%20old%20and%20valuable%20or%20rare%20objects.%E2%80%9D%20Antiquarianism%20historically%20has%20often%20had%20a%20negative%20connotation%2C%20as%20someone%20in%20an%20almost%20%E2%80%98mindless%E2%80%99%20pursuit%20of%20collecting%20objects%20and%20committed%20to%20the%20minute%20details%20of%20it.%20Historian%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20is%20someone%20who%20narrativised%20the%20past%2C%20with%20the%20focus%20on%20writing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHistorian%20Rosemary%20Sweet%20notes%20that%20history%20writing%20could%20be%20done%20for%20political%20or%20polemical%20purposes%20while%20antiquarians%20prided%20themselves%20to%20be%20impartial%20and%20staying%20true%20to%20the%20material.%20Antiquarians%20are%20often%20interested%20even%20in%20objects%20of%20everyday%20life%20which%20was%20not%20of%20interest%20to%20historians.%20Interestingly%2C%20Sweet%20points%20out%20that%20the%20contemporary%20practice%20of%20history%2C%20associated%20with%20archival%20study%2C%20which%20relies%20on%20the%20details%20presented%20by%20historical%20artefacts%20is%20very%20close%20to%20antiquarianism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20searching%20for%20these%20variety%20of%20terms%2C%20I%20am%20still%20left%20with%20no%20word%20to%20capture%20the%20affective%20engagement%20with%20history%20which%20I%20experienced%20in%20the%20office%20of%20Ansari%2C%20where%20history%20is%20not%20just%20a%20vocation%20or%20a%20profession%2C%20where%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20at%20stake%20in%20telling%20stories%20of%20the%20past%2C%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20one%E2%80%99s%20earnings.%20This%20voice%20of%20history%20is%20not%20a%20dispassionate%2C%20distant%20evaluation%20of%20the%20past%2C%20but%20is%20an%20expression%20of%20belongingness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeeply%20personal%20work%20like%20this%20has%20larger%20social%20implications%2C%20it%20is%20about%20communities%20taking%20the%20ownership%20of%20their%20own%20history%2C%20and%20inculcating%20historical%20consciousness%20among%20themselves.%20Such%20efforts%20go%20a%20long%20way%20in%20forming%20the%20first%20line%20of%20defence%20against%20vilification%20of%20history%20and%20weaponisation%20of%20history%20for%20political%20gains%2C%20of%20which%20we%20are%20seeing%20increasing%20incidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EC.%20Yamini%20Krishna%20works%20on%20film%20history%2C%20urban%20history%20and%20Deccan%20history.%20She%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Khidki%20collective.%20She%20currently%20teaches%20at%20FLAME%20University.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20work%20was%20done%20as%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Foundation%20Project%20is%20implemented%20by%20India%20Foundation%20for%20the%20Arts%20(IFA)%20under%20the%20Arts%20Research%20programme%2C%20made%20possible%20with%20support%20from%20BNP%20Paribas%20India.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710586543000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F16161042%2FScreen-Shot-2024-03-16-at-4.10.16-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2F