Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20our%20cotton%20clothes%20are%20made%20from%20natural%20colours%20that%20last%20forever%20and%20are%20also%20good%20for%20the%20skin.%20We%20make%20colours%20from%20turmeric%2C%20leaves%20from%20plants%20and%20a%20few%20vegetables%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jaison%20Bhramo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJyotisankar%20Sahu%20of%20the%20Sabar%20tribe%20from%20Odisha%20is%20here%20for%20the%20second%20time.%20For%20him%2C%20the%20best%20benefit%20of%20putting%20up%20a%20stall%20is%20making%20his%20digital%20debut.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20a%20group%20of%2070%20people%20who%20make%20brass%20showpieces.%20We%20always%20get%20orders%20after%20we%20return%20home%20from%20the%20conclave.%20Samvaad%20is%20a%20good%20platform%20to%20preserve%20our%20culture%20and%20tell%20the%20world%20about%20the%20exceptional%20skills%20that%20we%20learnt%20from%20our%20ancestors%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20exposure%2C%20the%20artisans%20are%20also%20happy%20to%20see%20people%20taking%20an%20interest%20in%20their%20traditions.%20Sangeeta%20Meda%20from%20the%20Bhil%20tribe%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20our%20second%20time%20here%2C%20and%20people%20always%20ask%20us%20about%20our%20history%20and%20the%20significance%20of%20our%20Bhil%20Pithora%20paintings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20ancestors%20would%20make%20these%20dotted%20paintings%20on%20walls%20during%20festivities.%20Gradually%2C%20they%20moved%20onto%20paper.%20Our%20paintings%20tell%20the%20stories%20of%20our%20origin%20and%20who%20we%20are.%20While%20selling%2C%20we%20let%20the%20customers%20know%20our%20intention%20behind%20choosing%20a%20particular%20colour%20and%20theme.%20They%20feel%20connected%20to%20us.%20My%20grandmother%2C%20Buri%20Bai%2C%20was%20awarded%20Padma%20Shri%20for%20her%20preservation%20efforts.%20We%20are%20here%20to%20carry%20forward%20her%20legacy%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESangeeta%20shares%20that%20the%20family%20starts%20the%20work%20nearly%20eight%20months%20before%20Samvaad%20as%20it%20takes%2010%20days%20to%20make%20one%20painting.%20She%20happily%20adds%20that%20their%20paintings%20sell%20like%20hotcakes!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsankalp_foundation_warli_art_11zon-1710328090-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20stall%20displaying%20products%20featuring%20Warli%20art.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsankalp_foundation_warli_art_11zon-1710328090-scaled.jpg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsankalp_foundation_warli_art_11zon-1710328090-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsankalp_foundation_warli_art_11zon-1710328090-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsankalp_foundation_warli_art_11zon-1710328090-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsankalp_foundation_warli_art_11zon-1710328090-1536x864.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsankalp_foundation_warli_art_11zon-1710328090-2048x1152.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsankalp_foundation_warli_art_11zon-1710328090-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344727%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20stall%20displaying%20various%20products%20featuring%20Warli%20art.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20stalls%20away%20is%20Dinabandhu%20Soren%20from%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20Ho%20tribe.%20It%20is%20his%20ninth%20year%20at%20Samvaad%2C%20and%20each%20year%20has%20been%20fruitful%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSelling%20our%20paintings%20was%20a%20loss-making%20business%20in%20Ganjam%20district%20till%20we%20learnt%20about%20Samvaad.%20The%20workshops%20helped%20create%20a%20balance%20between%20our%20traditional%20painting%20techniques%20and%20the%20market%20demands.%20With%20a%20few%20tweaks%20and%20the%20right%20market%20linkages%2C%20we%20sold%20%3Cem%3Egond%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Esohra%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Ejuang%3C%2Fem%3E%20paintings%20at%20Samvaad%20and%20across%20India.%20We%20were%20even%20selected%20to%20do%20live%20sketching%20at%20G20%20this%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Soren.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20also%20an%20art%20teacher%20at%20Srujanika%2C%20a%20women-led%20self-help%20group.%20Srujanika%20has%2030%20women%20who%20make%20paintings%2C%20Army%20uniforms%2C%20and%20other%20merchandise%20like%20%3Cem%3Edupattas%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20T-shirts%20throughout%20the%20year.%20Thanks%20to%20the%20profits%2C%20the%20women%20are%20passing%20on%20the%20skills%20to%20their%20children%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYazile%20from%20Nagaland%E2%80%99s%20Rengma%20tribe%20has%20a%20similar%20journey%2C%20from%20no%20sales%20to%20selling%20pan%20India.%20%E2%80%9CNearly%20every%20homemaker%20in%20the%20Dimapur%20area%20can%20make%20our%20traditional%20attire%2C%20%3Cem%3Emekhelas%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20shawls.%20The%20skills%20were%20there%2C%20but%20the%20selling%20opportunity%20was%20missing.%20We%20attended%20a%20workshop%20at%20Samvaad%20and%20learned%20that%20new%20designs%20can%20be%20implemented%20on%20pillow%20covers%2C%20cushion%20covers%2C%20T-shirts%2C%20etc.%20In%20our%20second%20year%2C%20we%20did%20that%20and%20made%20profits.%20I%20also%20made%20friends%20from%20other%20tribal%20communities%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20fashion%20trends%20across%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Yazile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20art%20and%20craft%20workshops%20helped%20artists%20like%20Yazile%20and%20Dinabandhu%20post-pandemic%20when%20the%20market%20crashed%20and%20selling%20at%20local%20%3Cem%3Ehaats%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebecame%20impossible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20building%20online%20market%20links%20for%2026%20tribal%20communities%20representing%2030%20art%20forms.%20We%20wanted%20to%20make%20%3Cem%3EToda%3C%2Fem%3E%20embroidery%20of%20Nilgiris%2C%20%3Cem%3EMuga%20%3C%2Fem%3Esilk%20of%20Assam%2C%20and%20more%20as%20popular%20as%20%3Cem%3EBanarasi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EIkat%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EChikankari%3C%2Fem%3E.%20We%20brought%20in%20experts%20from%20NIFT%20and%20NID%20to%20impart%20the%20skills%2C%20colour%20combinations%2C%20motifs%2C%20etc%2C%20that%20meet%20customer%20demands%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Smita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CTrends%20in%20the%20metro%20change%20fast%2C%20so%20we%20ask%20them%20not%20to%20change%20their%20cultural%20identity.%C2%A0%20But%20they%20can%20experiment%20with%20colours%20and%20motifs.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20pastel%20colour%20is%20in%20the%20market%2C%20infuse%20those%20colours%20in%20the%20products%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20thronging%20crowds%20at%20handicraft%20stalls%20were%20proof%20that%20the%20workshops%20were%20beneficial.%20Chaaya%20Saraiwala%2C%20an%20attendee%2C%20purchased%20Yazile%E2%80%99s%20shawls%20and%20Brijesh%E2%80%99s%20fridge%20magnets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20my%20first%20time%20attending%20Samvaad%20and%20I%20am%20so%20happy%20to%20see%20the%20myriad%20products%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20our%20country.%20I%20have%20bought%20a%20few%20items%20for%20my%20family.%20Each%20product%20has%20a%20story%20to%20tell.%20There%20is%20so%20much%20history%20that%20we%20do%20not%20know%2C%20but%20I%20am%20glad%20that%20conclaves%20like%20Samvaad%20are%20changing%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%20courtesy%3A%20Samvaad%20by%20Tata%20Steel%20Foundation)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710249302000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_0955-1710328096.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D344574%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20the%20Tata%20Samvaad%20conclave%20in%20Jamshedpur%2C%20artisans%20from%20indigenous%20tribes%20across%20India%20shone%20a%20spotlight%20on%20fading%20tribal%20arts%2C%20reviving%20them%20with%20contemporary%20flair%20to%20build%20livelihoods.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Gopi%20Karelia%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344574%2Ftata-samvaad-tribal-conclave-preserves-lost-heritage-artisans-sell-handicrafts%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trader%20Joe%E2%80%99s%20Threatened%20Workers%20Ahead%20Of%20Union%20Vote%2C%20Feds%20Allege%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22Labor%20board%20officials%20have%20accused%20the%20grocer%20of%20using%20illegal%20tactics%20to%20sway%20workers%20against%20unionizing.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710209921000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fimg.huffingtonpost.com%2Fasset%2F65a2ecd0240000310027f382.jpeg%3Fcache%3Dg8sPa742ew%26ops%3D1200_630%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Ftrader-joes-accused-threatening-workers-labor-board_n_65ef8ab2e4b05cfcf680b337%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Labor%20board%20officials%20have%20accused%20the%20grocer%20of%20using%20illegal%20tactics%20to%20sway%20workers%20against%20unionizing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A265%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Ftrader-joes-accused-threatening-workers-labor-board_n_65ef8ab2e4b05cfcf680b337%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-huffpost-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Ftrader-joes-accused-threatening-workers-labor-board_n_65ef8ab2e4b05cfcf680b337%2Famp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Ftrader-joes-accused-threatening-workers-labor-board_n_65ef8ab2e4b05cfcf680b337%2Famp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20a%20Unique%20Conclave%20Celebrates%20The%20Cultural%20Wealth%20of%20200%20Tribes%20of%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20has%20been%20published%20in%20partnership%20with%20Samvaad%20%E2%80%93%20Enabled%20by%20Tata%20Steel%20Foundation%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStanding%20next%20to%20women%20dressed%20in%20colourful%20sarees%2C%20Pritesh%20Kumar%20Khalko%20looked%20out%20of%20place%20at%20first%20in%20his%20black%20jacket%20at%20Jamshedpur%E2%80%99s%20Gopal%20Maidan.%20He%20looked%20tired%2C%20but%20that%20did%20not%20stop%20him%20from%20excitedly%20inviting%20strangers%20to%20his%20food%20stall%20and%20narrating%20the%20fascinating%20story%20behind%20each%20dish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20%3Cem%3Ebaas%3C%2Fem%3E%20(bamboo)%20pickle%20is%20good%20for%20your%20blood%2C%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehau%20%3C%2Fem%3Echutney%20made%20from%20red%20weaver%20ants%20is%20rich%20in%20protein%20and%20calcium.%20%3Cem%3EJamun%20%3C%2Fem%3Epowder%20helps%20control%20sugar%3B%20you%20will%20not%20find%20this%20anywhere%20else%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20the%20potential%20customer%20at%20his%20stall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conviction%20in%20his%20tone%20changed%20as%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20team%20asked%20about%20how%20his%20community%20cuisine%20could%20help%20his%20tribe%20do%20better.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CProvide%20us%20platforms%20like%20Samvaad%20where%20we%20can%20share%20our%20culture%20and%20food%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20help%20us%20tell%20our%20own%20stories%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPritesh%E2%80%99s%20focus%20on%20preserving%20his%20tribal%20identity%20through%20cuisine%20mirrored%20the%20essence%20of%20Samvaad%20%E2%80%94%20Enabled%20by%20Tata%20Steel%20Foundation%20(TSF)%2C%20which%20brings%20together%20the%20diverse%20tribes%20of%20India%20on%20one%20platform%20for%20a%20five-day-long%20festivity%2C%20which%20lets%20everyone%20immerse%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F274494%2Fgond-artist-artwork-museums-france-usa-uk%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etribal%20art%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20traditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPritesh%20belongs%20to%20one%20of%20the%20200%20tribal%20communities%20participating%20in%20Samvaad%20%E2%80%94%20a%20major%20tribal%20conclave%20which%20brings%20together%20tribes%20of%20the%20nation%20and%20beyond.%20It%20is%20emerging%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20most%20prominent%20platforms%20for%20dialogues%20on%20tribal%20discourse%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FGopal_Maidan_performance_11zon-1710165483-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Performance%20at%20Samvaad%20on%20Gopal%20Maidan%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FGopal_Maidan_performance_11zon-1710165483-scaled.jpg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FGopal_Maidan_performance_11zon-1710165483-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FGopal_Maidan_performance_11zon-1710165483-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FGopal_Maidan_performance_11zon-1710165483-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FGopal_Maidan_performance_11zon-1710165483-1536x864.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FGopal_Maidan_performance_11zon-1710165483-2048x1152.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FGopal_Maidan_performance_11zon-1710165483-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344566%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20tribal%20performance%20during%20Samvaad%20at%20Gopal%20Maidan.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EStrengthening%20the%20footprints%20of%20tribal%20identity%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%2013%20elements%20of%20Samvaad%2C%20which%20have%20emerged%20over%20the%20years%2C%20creating%20a%20permanent%20space%20for%20dialogue%20and%20conversations%20that%20are%20poised%20to%20tackle%20some%20of%20the%20challenges%20that%20lie%20ahead.%20This%20annual%20conclave%20not%20only%20celebrates%20tribal%20art%20and%20culture%20but%20also%20fosters%20dialogue%20to%20drive%20change%20in%20rural%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeld%20from%2015%20to%2019%20November%20each%20year%2C%20Samvaad%20honours%20the%20legacy%20of%20Birsa%20Munda%20%E2%80%94%20a%20tribal%20independence%20activist%20and%20leader%20from%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20Munda%20tribe.%20In%20its%20tenth%20year%2C%20themed%20%E2%80%98Walk%20with%20Me%E2%80%99%2C%20Samvaad%20reflected%20on%20a%20decade%20of%20impactful%20dialogues%2C%20recognising%20the%20journey%20of%20ideas%20and%20changemakers%20shaping%20the%20present%20and%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20different%20elements%20of%20Samvaad%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F161926%2Fandhra-pradesh-araku-coffee-gold-paris-news%2F%5C%22%3Eincluding%20f%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F161926%2Fandhra-pradesh-araku-coffee-gold-paris-news%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eo%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F161926%2Fandhra-pradesh-araku-coffee-gold-paris-news%2F%5C%22%3Eod%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20music%2C%20artisans%2C%20cultural%20markers%2C%20and%20others%2C%20bring%20a%20lot%20of%20intangible%20potential%20through%20this%20tribal%20cultural%20conclave.%20It%20is%20not%20only%20a%20platform%20of%20expression%20but%20also%20a%20forum%20for%20meaningful%20dialogues%20that%20add%20perspectives%20to%20the%20different%20aspects%20of%20life%20and%20one%E2%80%99s%20journey%20through%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sourav%20Roy%2C%20CEO%20of%20TSF.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continued%2C%20%E2%80%9CThroughout%20the%20year%2C%20we%20engage%20with%20the%20tribes%20through%20our%20initiatives%20to%20converge%20on%20dialogues%20that%20set%20the%20tone%20for%20Samvaad%20each%20year.%20Many%20new%20ideas%20and%20innovations%20emerge%20from%20these%20conversations%2C%20moderated%20by%20experts%20from%20respective%20fields%20and%20changemakers%20from%20all%20over%20the%20country.%20Celebration%20of%20culture%20also%20forms%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20Samvaad%2C%20which%20not%20only%20generates%20livelihood%20for%20tribal%20artisans%20but%20also%20allows%20people%20to%20appreciate%20their%20unique%20traditions%2C%20passed%20down%20through%20generations%2C%20rich%20in%20wisdom.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESamvaad%E2%80%99s%20varied%20ecosystem%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20magnitude%20of%20Samvaad%20is%20reflected%20in%20its%20diverse%20ecosystem%2C%20which%20includes%20promoting%20tribal%20healers%2C%20artisans%2C%20cuisines%2C%20languages%2C%20sports%20and%20heritage%20conservation%2C%20%3Cem%3EAkhra%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3ESamudaay%20ke%20Saath%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Rhythms%20of%20the%20Earth%2C%20Tribal%20Leadership%20Programme%2C%20Samvaad%20Fellowship%2C%20and%20Samvaad%20Action%20Research%20Collective.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Samvaad%20Fellowship%20aims%20to%20guide%20and%20nurture%20individuals%20committed%20to%20preserving%20tribal%20culture%20and%20heritage%20through%20community-based%20action.%20After%20a%20round%20of%20assessments%2C%20the%20fellows%20receive%20one-year%20grants%20and%20mentorships%20from%20academicians%20and%20experts.%20These%20fellowships%20have%20led%20to%20tangible%20outcomes%20like%20tribal%20dictionaries%2C%20song%20recordings%2C%20story%20books%20for%20children%2C%20collectives%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20contesting%20elections%20to%20making%20documentaries%20on%20tribal%20issues%2C%20many%20people%20have%20emerged%20as%20leaders%20and%20changemakers.%20Some%20have%20even%20failed.%20Irrespective%20of%20your%20failure%20or%20success%2C%20you%20have%20made%20friends%20who%20will%20always%20support%20you.%20And%20that%20is%20what%20Samvaad%20aims%20to%20be%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jiren%20Xavier%20Topno%2C%20Head%20of%20Tribal%20Identity%20at%20TSF.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201915px)%20100vw%2C%201915px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fakhra3_11zon-1710165480.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221915%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Participants%20at%20the%20Akhra%20event%20in%20Samvaad%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fakhra3_11zon-1710165480.jpg%201915w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fakhra3_11zon-1710165480-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fakhra3_11zon-1710165480-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fakhra3_11zon-1710165480-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fakhra3_11zon-1710165480-1536x864.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fakhra3_11zon-1710165480-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344565%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221077%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EParticipants%20at%20the%20Akhra%20event%20in%20Samvaad.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamvaad%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3E10tak%20at%20Akhra%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20is%20another%20way%20in%20which%20the%20conclave%20served%20as%20a%20platform%20where%20individuals%20from%20diverse%20tribal%20groups%20came%20together%20to%20share%20their%20journey%20of%20change%2C%20challenges%2C%20and%20possible%20solutions.%20As%20Samvaad%20stepped%20into%20its%20tenth%20year%2C%20over%20500%20people%20gathered%20to%20share%20their%20inspiring%20stories%20at%20the%20open-air%20Amphitheatre%20at%20the%20Tribal%20Cultural%20Centre%20(TCC).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAakash%20Pawar%2C%20instigated%20by%20the%20rising%20farmer%20suicides%20across%20Maharashtra%2C%20fought%20for%20his%20rights%20and%20now%20runs%20constitution%20schools%20to%20educate%20his%20community%20about%20their%20rights%3B%20Manasi%20from%20Odisha%20helped%20bring%20back%20thousands%20of%20migrant%20labourers%20amid%20the%20pandemic%20by%20being%20a%20citizen%20journalist%3B%20and%20Garima%20Siddhar%20is%20a%20lawyer%20providing%20justice%20to%20tribal%20communities.%20These%20changemakers%20are%20now%20a%20part%20of%20the%20tribal%20leadership%20programme%20alumni%2C%20which%20is%20over%20400-%20members%20strong%2C%20who%20have%20stayed%20connected%20to%20share%20their%20narratives%20of%20change%20to%20inspire%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20cultural%20lens%2C%20Samvaad%20organises%20a%20grand%20inaugural%20show%20every%20year%20at%20Gopal%20Maidan.%20This%20year%2C%20251%20%3Cem%3Enagadas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Edhols%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20musical%20instruments%20reverberated%20in%20homage%20to%20Birsa%20Munda.%20The%20tribals%20adorning%20bright%20yellow%20vests%20with%20white%20%3Cem%3Edhotis%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20played%20various%20goosebump-inducing%20songs%20%E2%80%94%20from%20the%20%3Cem%3Ebonga%20taal%2C%20baika%20taal%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3Esantal%20taal%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDancers%20and%20singers%20participated%20in%20cultural%20performances%20as%20people%20gorged%20on%20tribal%20delicacies%2C%20shopped%20for%20vibrant%20artefacts%20(handcrafted%20by%20the%20same%20artisans%20who%20are%20selling%20them)%2C%20and%20danced%20to%20the%20tribal%20beats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20my%20tenth%20year%20and%20I%20have%20been%20a%20part%20of%20Samvaad%20since%20the%20beginning.%20I%20love%20the%20energy%20here.%20Of%20course%2C%20the%20highlight%20is%20selling%20our%20Oraon%20paintings%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sumanti%20Devi%2C%20a%20painter%20from%20Chhattisgarh.%20%E2%80%9CVery%20few%20people%20knew%20about%20our%20paintings%20before%2C%20but%20now%20it%20is%20more%20popular.%20Initially%2C%20it%20was%20only%20handicrafts%20stalls%2C%20but%20Samvaad%20has%20grown%20so%20much%20with%20%3Cem%3EAkhara%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20fellowship%2C%20tribal%20healers%2C%20Tribal%20Leadership%20Programme%20and%20more.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Choisa%20Hakong%20from%20the%20Chakesang%20tribe%20(Nagaland)%20was%20at%20the%20conclave%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20%E2%80%9CSamvaad%20is%20connecting%20tribals%20as%20one%20in%20spirit%20and%20culture.%20I%20am%20so%20happy%20to%20attend%20and%20showcase%20our%20products%20made%20from%20teak%20and%20bamboo%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20five%20days%2C%20Pritesh%2C%20Sumanti%2C%20and%20Choisa%2C%20along%20with%20people%20from%20110%20other%20tribes%2C%20displayed%20their%20cuisine%2C%20artwork%2C%20and%20healing%20practices.%20Besides%20the%20stalls%2C%20140%20home%20chefs%20from%2037%20tribes%20offered%20home%20delivery%20via%20the%20Zomato%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20role%20of%20these%20artisans%20goes%20beyond%20selling%20their%20products.%20They%20also%20refine%20their%20skills%20through%20workshops%20and%20sessions%20led%20by%20handicraft%20experts%2C%20engage%20in%20healing%20practices%2C%20and%20showcase%20their%20culinary%20talents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPritesh_Kumar_Khalko_para_1._11zon-1710165476-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tribal%20food%20at%20display%20in%20one%20of%20the%20stalls%20at%20Samvaad.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPritesh_Kumar_Khalko_para_1._11zon-1710165476-scaled.jpg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPritesh_Kumar_Khalko_para_1._11zon-1710165476-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPritesh_Kumar_Khalko_para_1._11zon-1710165476-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPritesh_Kumar_Khalko_para_1._11zon-1710165476-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPritesh_Kumar_Khalko_para_1._11zon-1710165476-1536x864.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPritesh_Kumar_Khalko_para_1._11zon-1710165476-2048x1152.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPritesh_Kumar_Khalko_para_1._11zon-1710165476-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344564%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETribal%20food%20displayed%20in%20one%20of%20the%20stalls%20at%20Samvaad.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20tangible%20difference%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20over%20the%20last%20decade%20of%20Samvaad%2C%20the%20initiative%20has%20seen%20a%20visible%20impact%2C%20bringing%20together%20over%2040%2C000%20people%20from%20India%20and%2017%20other%20countries.%20The%20beauty%20of%20this%20conclave%20is%20that%20it%20extends%20beyond%20the%20five%20days%3B%20the%20dialogue%20and%20actions%20continue%20throughout%20the%20year.%20This%20meticulous%20approach%20has%20led%20to%20outcomes%20that%20once%20seemed%20far-fetched.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%2C%20for%20example%2C%20%E2%80%98Rhythms%20of%20the%20Earth%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20an%20ensemble%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F121371%2Fanahad-tribal-music%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etribal%20musicians%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20across%20the%20country%20composed%20and%20launched%20five%20original%20compositions%20on%20a%20tribal%20narrative%20at%20the%20conclave.%20The%20compositions%20are%20on%20the%20theme%20of%20unifying%20tribals%20in%20the%20face%20of%20adversity.%20They%20include%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ENukhtharini%20Juwmang%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20Rabha%20tribe%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EEklaivet%20Ajakong%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20Karbi%20tribe%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EDela%20Dela%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20Santal%20tribe%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EAbua%20Disom%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20from%20the%20Ho%20tribe%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20significant%20outcome%20of%20Samvaad%E2%80%99s%20ten-year%20journey%20was%20seen%20in%20Jaincy%20John%E2%80%99s%20struggle%20to%20break%20away%20from%20the%20conventional%20narrative%20of%20urban%20education.%20Living%20in%20cities%20often%20limits%20our%20view%20of%20education%20to%20securing%20future%20jobs.%20However%2C%20for%20those%20in%20remote%20areas%20far%20from%20mainstream%20society%2C%20education%20is%20about%20identity%20and%20challenging%20stereotypes%20built%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20academician%20and%20activist%20from%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20Mala%20Arya%20community%2C%20Jaincy%20challenged%20the%20stereotypes%20around%20tribal%20identity.%20While%20she%20was%20working%20on%20extensive%20pieces%20on%20Adivasi%20and%20Dalit%20art%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20history%2C%20and%20completing%20her%20PhD%2C%20she%20encountered%20discrimination%20and%20abuse%20from%20her%20guide.%20However%2C%20that%20did%20not%20deter%20her%20from%20her%20path.%20She%20filed%20a%20complaint%20against%20him%2C%20which%20further%20helped%20other%20women%20open%20up%20about%20their%20similar%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Jancy%20continues%20to%20fight%20the%20legal%20battle%2C%20Samvaad%20has%20supported%20the%20right%20of%20many%20tribal%20members%20to%20represent%20themselves%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F212493%2Ftata-steel-india-tribe-conclave-samvaad-jamshedpur-jharkhand%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENothing%20about%20us%20without%20us%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20important%20because%20tribal%20individuals%20deserve%20recognition%20as%20prominent%20leaders%2C%20and%20Samvaad%20is%20dedicated%20to%20amplifying%20their%20visibility.%20The%20conclave%20advocates%20for%20inclusivity%20and%20equality%2C%20ensuring%20that%20everyone%20has%20a%20voice%20and%20uniting%20those%20who%20have%20faced%20exploitation%20due%20to%20their%20identity.%20Today%2C%20members%20of%20tribal%20communities%20are%20not%20simply%20demanding%20a%20seat%20at%20the%20table%3B%20they%20are%20actively%20forging%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%20courtesy%3A%20Samvaad%20by%20Tata%20Steel%20Foundation)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710164862000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FGopal_Maidan_performance_11zon-1710165483-scaled.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D344526%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tata%20Samvaad%2C%20enabled%20by%20the%20Tata%20Steel%20Foundation%20in%20Jharkhand%2C%20brings%20together%20200%20tribal%20communities%20annually%20to%20celebrate%20their%20rich%20culture%20and%20identity%20through%20art%2C%20food%2C%20workshops%2C%20and%20conversations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Gopi%20Karelia%22%2C%22engageme