who%20have%20adeptly%20managed%20the%20finances.%20This%20tradition%20has%20persisted%20in%20my%20own%20family%2C%20spanning%20over%20three%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20grandfather%20would%20entrust%20his%20salary%20to%20my%20grandmother%2C%20who%20skillfully%20managed%20the%20modest%20sum%2C%20even%20though%20it%20was%20in%20the%20mere%20three%20digits%20during%20the%201950s.%20Similarly%2C%20my%20father%20would%20hand%20over%20his%20paycheck%20to%20my%20mother%2C%20and%20together%20they%20would%20make%20informed%20decisions%20on%20how%20to%20invest%20their%20savings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prudent%20financial%20practices%20of%20our%20grandmothers%2C%20mothers%2C%20and%20mothers-in-law%20have%20proven%20invaluable%20during%20challenging%20times%2C%20such%20as%20health%20crises%20or%20job%20losses.%20Their%20careful%20stewardship%20has%20not%20only%20ensured%20stability%20but%20also%20enabled%20significant%20investments%20like%20purchasing%20homes%20and%20vehicles%20%E2%80%94%20a%20feat%20accomplished%20without%20relying%20on%20prevalent%20practices%2C%20such%20as%20loans%20and%20EMIs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECut%20to%20today%E2%80%99s%20era%2C%20when%20managing%20finances%20has%20become%20increasingly%20complex%2C%20who%20better%20to%20guide%20us%20than%20women%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavigating%20personal%20finances%20and%20mastering%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F339578%2Fradhika-gupta-shark-tank-india-judge-edelweiss-asset-management-broken-neck-ceo%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprudent%20investment%20strategies%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20intricate%20skill%20that%20demands%20diligent%20study.%20And%20with%20a%20plethora%20of%20financial%20tools%20and%20avenues%20available%2C%20simply%20stashing%20away%20cash%20at%20home%20is%20no%20longer%20sufficient.%20Our%20financial%20aspirations%20have%20evolved%2C%20encompassing%20everything%20from%20retirement%20planning%20to%20annual%2