20single-use%20plastic%20bottled%20water.%20The%20reject%20from%20the%20RO%20plant%20is%20used%20in%20the%20garden%20and%20has%20been%20tested%20to%20be%20fit%20for%20this%20purpose%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resort%20has%20a%20host%20of%20activities%20that%20their%20guests%20can%20enjoy%20%E2%80%94%20including%20tree%20walks%2C%20bird%20trails%2C%20Kalapathar%20beach%20trek%2C%20Elephant%20beach%20trek%2C%20scuba%20diving%2C%20snorkelling%2C%20kayaking%2C%20and%20standup%20paddling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20number%20of%20guests%2C%20the%20resort%2C%20the%20dive%20centre%2C%20and%20the%20travel%20company%20have%20collectively%20hosted%20over%20two%20to%20three%20lakh%20people%20since%20it%20opened%20its%20doors%2C%20says%20Samit.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20welcome%20about%2010%2C000%20tourists%20a%20year.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjay%20who%20visited%20the%20property%20in%202024%20calls%20it%20%E2%80%9Ca%20hidden%20slice%20of%20heaven%E2%80%9D.%20He%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20the%20moment%20you%20arrive%2C%20the%20Barefoot%20crew%20greets%20you%20with%20the%20warmest%20of%20welcomes.%20They%E2%80%99re%20all%20about%20fostering%20a%20sense%20of%20kinship%2C%20and%20let%20me%20assure%20you%2C%20they%20succeed%20admirably.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20rooms%20are%20a%20fusion%20of%20luxury%20with%20a%20hint%20of%20Robinson%20Crusoe%20charm.%20However%2C%20what%20truly%20distinguishes%20Barefoot%20is%20its%20commitment%20to%20eco-friendliness.%20They%20prioritise%20sustainability%20without%20compromising%20on%20the%20finer%20things.%20From%20harnessing%20solar%20power%20to%20implementing%20waste%20reduction%20measures%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20as%20if%20they%E2%80%99re%20exchanging%20high-fives%20with%20Mother%20Nature%20while%20you%20indulge%20in%20your%20cocktail.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com