0a%20doctor%2C%20but%20life%20had%20other%20plans.%20Before%20she%20could%20complete%20her%20education%2C%20she%20was%20married.%20Soon%2C%20she%20had%20two%20children%20and%20life%20revolved%20around%20them.%20As%20the%20children%20started%20school%2C%20Poonam%20slowly%20restarted%20her%20education%20and%20pursued%20a%20BEd%20(Bachelor%20of%20Education)%20degree%20and%20entered%20a%20teacher%20training%20programme.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20she%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20pursue%20a%20career%20as%20a%20teacher.%20Busy%20with%20household%20chores%20and%20taking%20care%20of%20her%20family%2C%20she%20didn%E2%80%99t%20find%20the%20time%20to%20socialise%20or%20build%20a%20strong%20friend%E2%80%99s%20circle.%20So%20when%20her%20children%20left%20for%20hostel%20in%202018%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20reclaim%20her%20life%20and%20build%20a%20better%20future%20for%20the%20coming%20generations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20almost%20went%20through%20an%20existential%20crisis%2C%20she%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20just%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20to%20do.%20What%20was%20the%20purpose%20of%20my%20life%3F%20I%20was%20depressed%2C%20alone%2C%20without%20a%20clear%20trajectory%20of%20life.%20My%20mother%20asked%20me%20to%20visit%20a%20temple%20as%20she%20felt%20it%20would%20make%20me%20happy.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Pinky%2C%20too%2C%20was%20going%20through%20a%20tough%20time%20and%20asked%20me%20if%20we%20could%20do%20something%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Poonam%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20highlighted%20above%2C%20she%20found%20her%20answer%20at%20the%20temple%20that%20changed%20her%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20found%20that%20tonnes%20of%20flowers%20were%20being%20dumped%20into%20the%20river%20daily.%20I%20found%20a%20company%20that%20was%20recycling%20flowers%20and%20asked%20for%20their%20help.%20They%20asked%20for%20my%20profile%20and%20said%20that%20they%20would%20